20babies.%20%26quot%3BHard%20plastic%20baby%20toys%20and%20rattles%20are%20a%20favorite%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ratches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Berman's%20favorite%20options%20is%20The%20First%20Years%20First%20Keys.%20Weighing%20less%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20pound%2C%20this%20set%20features%20five%20keys%20strung%20on%20a%20plastic%20ring%20that%20is%20easy%20for%20a%20bunny%20to%20toss.%20Each%20key%20is%20a%20different%20color%20and%20shape%2C%20and%20you%20can%20easily%20remove%20each%20one%20from%20the%20ring.%20And%20while%20the%20hard%2C%20durable%20plastic%20isn't%20completely%20impenetrable%2C%20it's%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20prevent%20even%20the%20most%20zealous%20chewers%20from%20breaking%20off%20bits%20they%20could%20then%20swallow.%20Even%20so%2C%20supervision%20is%20always%20advisable%20when%20bunnies%20play%20with%20nondigestible%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20bunny%20hideaway%3A%20Willow%20Tent%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wicker%20triangular%20shape%20rabbit%20hideaway%20is%20shown%20in%20the%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F601c579a5f153c001979b449%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Willow%20Tent%20is%20a%20simple%20hideaway%20that%20is%20the%20best%20option%20for%20your%20bunny's%20indoor%20habitat.%3Cp%3EBinky%20Bunny%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20rabbit%20toys%20offer%20bunnies%20different%20types%20of%20play%2C%20and%20a%20tunnel%20is%20a%20versatile%20toy%20to%20add%20to%20your%20bunny's%20collection.%20Tunnels%20can%20provide%20rabbits%20with%20another%20form%20of%20shelter%20beyond%20their%20hutch%2C%20and%20they%20can%20also%20be%20a%20vessel%20for%20the%20rabbit%20to%20run%20through%20or%20jump%20onto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oxbow%20Timothy%20Tunnel%20is%20an%20ideal%20tunnel%20for%20any%20indoor%20rabbit%20habitat.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20h