0even%20if%20your%20bunny%20gets%20along%20with%20the%20cats%20and%20dogs%2C%20a%20space%20of%20their%20own%20can%20help%20them%20rest%20and%20recharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20want%20to%20provide%20your%20bunny%20with%20access%20to%20a%20long%20hallway%20or%20open%20space%20for%20running%2C%20jumping%2C%20and%20binkies%20(jumping%20twists%20a%20bunny%20does%20when%20happy).%20If%20your%20floors%20are%20bare%2C%20Berman%20recommends%20putting%20down%20nonslip%20flooring%20so%20your%20bunny%20can%20get%20traction%20as%20they%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20essentials%20include%20a%20wire%20exercise%20pen%20or%20large%20kennel%20for%20overnight%20stays%3B%20a%20litter%20box%20filled%20with%20a%20paper%20pellet%20litter%20or%20hay%20for%20toileting%3B%20multiple%20water%20bowls%3B%20hay%20or%20grass%20to%20chew%20(placing%20it%20inside%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_062618_best-rabbit-toys-20%26h%3D8f26bd45d19a3b4006def28199e2d710cc5d1430e5b9580f8d1d7e7e2305aa9f%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f41c48%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-rabbit-toys%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB005FU4Z8I%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526tag%253Dbiipg_071320_best-rabbit-toys-20%2526camp%253D1789%2526creative%253D9325%2526linkCode%253Das2%2526creativeASIN%253DB005FU4Z8I%2526linkId%253D5a72a9d76796359f43ef809e9ddd951b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehay%20holder%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20keep%20it%20clean%20and%20appetizing)%3B%20and%20rabbit%20food%20pellets%20and%20fresh%20or%20dried%20greens%2C%20veggies%2C%20or%20fruits%20for%20an%20extra%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20possible%2C%20adopting%20a%20second%20bunny%20is%20an%20excellent%20way%20to%20enrich%20your%20rabbit's%20life.%20%26quot%3BRabbits%20tend%20to%20do%20better%20in%20a%20pair%20because%20they%20have%20a%20bonded%20buddy%20for%20companionship%20and%20grooming%2C%26quot%