544d4d0ede300018c10994%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDandelion%20Chocolate%20Factory%3B%20iStock%3B%20Gilbert%20Espinoza%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20currently%20employed%20as%20a%20chocolatier%2C%20I've%20lived%20previous%20lives%20in%20both%20scientific%20research%20and%20recipe%20development.%20I'm%20a%20scientist%20at%20heart%20and%20a%20true%20chocolate-fanatic%2C%20so%20my%20testing%20approach%20for%20researching%20the%20best%20chocolate%20was%20both%20methodical%20and%20thorough.%20My%20education%20in%20the%20hard%20sciences%2C%20the%20savory%20culinary%20arts%2C%20and%20finally%20fine%20chocolatier-work%20has%20all%20been%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20daunting%20task%20of%20hand-selecting%20the%20very%20best%20chocolates.%20I%20cut%20no%20corners%20and%20left%20no%20truffle%20unturned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20by%20reading%20about%20top%20brands%20in%20the%20chocolate%20industry%2C%20then%20taste-tested%20countless%20confections%2C%20evaluating%20their%20flavors%2C%20textures%2C%20and%20presentation.%20In%20all%2C%20I%20sampled%20more%20than%2075%20products%20from%2036%20brands%20for%20this%20guide.%20Here%20is%20the%20criteria%20I%20considered%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlavor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20growing%20conditions%20of%20the%20cacao%20used%20to%20make%20any%20given%20chocolate%20impact%20its%20flavor%2C%20which%20can%20range%20from%20sweet%20and%20fruity%2C%20to%20nutty%20and%20toasty%2C%20to%20bitter%20or%20acidic.%20These%20can%20all%20be%20used%20effectively%20in%20different%20applications.%20However%2C%20chocolate%20that%20has%20gone%20bad%20or%20rancid%20will%20have%20a%20soapy%20or%20cheesy%20flavor.%20I%20looked%20for%20balanced%2C%20prominent%20cocoa%20notes%20with%20no%20off%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFreshness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20avoid%20sacrificing%20taste%2C%20presentation%2C%20and%20overall%20quality%2C%20it%20is