the%20best%20straightening%20brushes%20because%20it%20features%2010%20variable%20heat%20settings%2C%20and%20with%20the%20combination%20of%20warmth%20and%20the%20surface's%20ceramic%20coating%2C%20even%20dull%20hair%20will%20see%20a%20vast%20improvement%20in%20shine.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20an%20ion%20generator%20results%20in%20smoother%2C%20glossier%20strands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20curly%20hair%3Cp%3ETaming%20wild%20curls%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcelebrities-embrace-natural-hair-while-social-distancing-2020-4%5C%22%3Eif%20you%20so%20choose%3C%2Fa%3E)%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20but%20the%20Enhanced%20Hair%20Straightener%20Brush%20from%20MicroPure%20makes%20the%20process%20less%20taxing.%20According%20to%20the%2010%2C000%2B%20reviews%20on%20Amazon%20alone%2C%20MiroPure's%20straightening%20brush%20significantly%20reduces%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20those%20with%20curly%20hair%20types%20to%20straighten%20their%20hair.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20tight%20curls%2Fcoils%2C%20and%20this%20brush%20straightened%20better%20than%20my%20very%20expensive%20flat%20iron%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20reviewer.%20%26quot%3BIt%20only%20took%2016%20mins%20to%20do%20half%20of%20my%20hair!!%20I%20have%20never%20straightened%20my%20hair%20so%20quickly!%26quot%3B%20added%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MicroPure%20features%2016%20impressive%20heat%20settings%20that%20help%20every%20hair%20type%20get%20its%20ideal%20style.%20Still%2C%20the%20straightening%20brush%20is%20an%20especially%20great%20option%20for%20wavy%20and%20curly%20hair%20types%20as%20the%20high-density%20nano%20comb%20bristles%20efficiently%20work%20through%20coarse%20strands%2C%20and%20its%20double%20ionic%20generator%20seals%20the%20hair%20cuticles%2C%20resulting%20in%20smoother%2C%20more%20lustrous%20hair.%20Plus%2C%20less%20time%20styling%20means%20less%20heat%20exposure%2C%20so%20hair%20will%20look%20and%20feel%20silkier%2C%20not%20dry%20and%20sullen%2C%20by%20the%20time%20you're%20finished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20frizz%3Cp%3EGot%20frizz%2C%20poof%2C%20and%20flyaways%3F%20InStyler's%20straightening%20brush%20is%20the%20first%20on%20the%20market%20to%20boast%20as%20many%20ions%20as%20a%20blow%20dryer.%20It's%20these%20same%20ionic%20bristles%20that%20add%20a%20layer%20of%2C%20what%20the%20brand%20describes%20as%2C%20%26quot%3Bsuperior%20de-frizzing.%26quot%3B%20That%2C%20plus%20the%20brush's%20ceramic%20plate%20design%20(there%20are%2065%20in%20total)%2C%20adds%20up%20to%20one%20of%20the%20best%20straightening%20brushes%20built%20to%20smooth%20the%20most%20undulated%20strands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20reducing%20frizz%2C%20reviewers%20say%20the%20Straight%20Up%20Max%20Ionic%20Hot%20Brush%20is%20as%20quick%20as%20it%20is%20efficient%20in%20deflating%20poofy%20hair.%20%26quot%3BThis%20brush%20made%20my%20hair%20smooth%20and%20straight%20with%20one%20pass!%26quot%3B%20one%20reviewer%20raved%2C%20while%20another%20noted%20it%20makes%20their%20mornings%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%20easier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20fine%20and%20damaged%20hair%3Cp%3EHot%20tools%20can%20do%20a%20number%20on%20hair%20if%20you're%20not%20careful%20(or%20if%20you're%20not%20using%20the%20right%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-heat-protectant%5C%22%3Eheat%20protectant%20products%3C%2Fa%3E).%20If%20it%20feels%20like%20your%20strands%20are%20at%20the%20point%20of%20no%20return%2C%20there's%20good%20news%3A%20The%20TYMO%20Hair%20Straightener%20Brush%20lets%20you%20style%20your%20hair%20and%20heal%20it%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pink%20tool%20does%20more%20than%20look%20pretty%20on%20your%20vanity.%20The%20brush%20is%20designed%20with%20an%20ionic%20coating%20that%20releases%20millions%20of%20ions%20in%20tandem%20with%20heat%20to%20create%20a%20protective%20layer%20for%20hair.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20straightener%20operates%20on%20Positive%20Temperature%20Coefficient%20(PTC)%20heating%20technology.%20It%20heats%20the%20tool's%20large%20styling%20surface%20faster%2C%20so%20you%20can%20style%20more%20hair%20in%20a%20more%20timely%20manner.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20the%20TYMO%20Hair%20Straightener%20Brush%20takes%20our%20top%20spot%20for%20fine%20hair%20is%20because%20of%20its%20temperature%20setting%20options.%20Unlike%20other%20straightening%20brushes%2C%20the%20lowest%20setting%20on%20the%20TYMO%20styler%20is%20266%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20so%20even%20sensitive%20hair%20types%20can%20be%20styled%20with%20this%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETemperature%20guide%3Cp%3EStraightening%20brushes%20can%20also%20be%20used%20on%20all%20hair%20types.%20Lower%20temperatures%20are%20better%20for%20fine%20or%20damaged%20hair%2C%20and%20higher%20temperatures%20are%20best%20for%20thick%20or%20coarse%20hair.%20Here%20is%20a%20guide%20to%20help%20you%20work%20out%20the%20right%20temperature%20for%20you%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E300%C2%B0%20Fahrenheit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fine%2C%20thin%2C%20or%20damaged%20hair%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E360%C2%B0%20Fahrenheit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Curly%20or%20thick%20hair%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E430%C2%B0%20Fahrenheit(%2B)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20coarse%2C%20hard-to-style%20hair%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-straightening-brush%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702416417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61fae1a50042510018f41ace%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-straightening-brush%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Straightening%20brushes%20are%20a%20time-saving%20tool%20that%20can%20straighten%20hair%20without%20flattening%20volume.%20Get%20shiny%2C%20frizz-free%20hair%20with%20these%20best%20of%20the%20