r%2C%20which%20happened%20to%20be%20a%20very%20busy%20week%20for%20the%20chain.%20(The%20chain%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-compete-starbucks-drink-focused-cosmcs-launch-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficial%20details%20for%20its%20spinoff%20restaurant%20CosMc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-plans-unprecedented-new-restaurants-openings-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadd%2010%2C000%20restaurants%20to%20its%20fleet%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-chicken-wraps-return-menu-due-to-chicken-demand-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignaled%20it%20would%20bring%20back%20wraps.%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20confirming%20with%20the%20chain%20and%20franchisees%20that%20the%20stores%20we%20visited%20in%20Ohio%20and%20California%20had%20the%20new%20improvements%2C%20we%20set%20to%20work%20evaluating%20them.%20We%20focused%20on%20buns%2C%20cheese%2C%20onions%2C%20pickles%2C%20lettuce%2C%20sauce%2C%20and%20the%20burger%20itself%20using%20information%20the%20chain%20released%20as%20well%20as%20some%20details%20revealed%20in%20another%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20we%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222263%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Big%20Mac%20Bun%20upclose%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65787d807a3c8094d5dc0852%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221583%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20very%20soft%20bun.%3Cp%3EGloria%20Dawson%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcDonald's%20promised%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BSofter%2C%20pillowy%20buns%20that%20are%20freshly%20toasted%20to%20a%20golden%20brown.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhospitality%2Fmcdonalds-burger-new-menu-2400d22b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20the%20bun%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20buttery%20brioche%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bsesame%20seeds%20more%20randomly%20scattered%20for%20a%20homemade%20look.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloria%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20buns%20are%20definitely%20soft.%20It%20dimpled%20under%20my%20finger%20when%20I%20held%20the%20Big%20Mac%20out%20to%20take%20a%20photo.%20The%20buns%20may%20have%20been%20inching%20toward%20too%20soft.%20The%20Big%20Macs%20I%20tried%20were%20difficult%20to%20eat%20without%20falling%20apart.%20The%20scattered%20sesame%20seeds%20were%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENancy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPresentation-wise%2C%20it%20looked%20great%20with%20the%20new%20pillowy%20bun%2C%20which%20was%20warm%20to%20the%20touch.%20Sometimes%20McDonald's%20buns%20can%20be%20cold.%20Still%2C%20McDonald's%20said%20they%20are%20using%20a%20buttery%20brioche%20bun%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20any%20butter%20in%20the%20flavorless%20bun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESauce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Presentation-wise%2C%20the%20Big%20Mac%20looked%20great.%20it%20did%20deliver%20on%20the%20extra%20sauce.%20Maybe%20too%20much.%20It%20was%20dripping%20down%20my%20chin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65710bf80ec98e92f74cfc4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20did%20deliver%20on%20the%20extra%20sauce.%20Maybe%20too%20much.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcDonald's%20promised%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BEven%20more%20of%20everyone's%20favorite%20Big%20Mac%20sauce%2C%20bringing%20more%20tangy%20sweetness%20in%20every%20Big%20Mac%20bite.%20The%20special%20sauce%20is%20bumped%20up%20to%20half%20an%20ounce%20from%20one-third.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloria%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20was%20a%20ton%20of%20sauce%20on%20the%20Big%20Macs.%20I%20got%20the%20feeling%20the%20sauce%20was%20trying%20to%20hide%20that%20the%20burger%20was%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENancy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20I%20took%20a%20bite%2C%20the%20sauce%20began%20oozing%20out%20of%20the%20burger%20like%20toothpaste%20from%20a%20tube.%20The%20corner%20of%20my%20lip%20and%20part%20of%20my%20chin%20was%20covered%20in%20sauce.%20(See%20pic%20above)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnions%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20lettuce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Big%20Mac%20with%20lots%20of%20lettuce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65787a4558e7c0c29a2c06cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224005%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20little%20overboard%20with%20the%20lettuce.%3Cp%3EGloria%20Dawson%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcDonald's%20promised%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BJuicier%2C%20caramelized%20flavor%20from%20adding%20white%20onions%20to%20the%20patties%20while%20they're%20still%20on%20the%20grill.%26quot%3B%20The%20chain%20told%20the%20Journal%20the%20onions%20were%20dehydrated%20after%20harvesting%20and%20rehydrated%20in%20the%20restaurant%20and%20%26quot%3Bdispensed%20through%20plastic%20shakers%20onto%20burgers%20as%20they%20cook.%26quot%3B%20The%20lettuce%20and%20pickles%20were%20expected%20to%20be%20fresher%20than%20previous%20burgers%20as%20they%20were%20stored%20in%20smaller%20containers%2C%20%26quot%3Brequiring%20crews%20to%20refresh%20them%20from%20the%20cooler%20more%20often.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloria%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20saw%20haphazard%20onion%20distribution%20with%20no%20noticeable%20flavor.%20The%20opposite%20happened%20with%20the%20lettuce.%20There%20was%20so%20much!%20The%20extreme%20amount%20of%20lettuce%20made%20the%20Big%20Mac%20messier.%20Between%20the%20sauce%20and%20the%20lettuce%2C%20the%20burgers%20were%20sliding%20around%2C%20and%20the%20super%20soft%20bun%20couldn't%20hold%20it%20all%20in%20place.%20The%20pickles%2C%20however%2C%20offered%20a%20perfect%20sour%20crunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENancy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20was%20a%20paltry%20amount%20of%20tiny%20chopped%20onions%20on%20the%20top%20patty%20of%20my%20Big%20Mac.%20If%20they%20want%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20grill%20onions%20with%20a%20burger%2C%20they%20should%20check%20out%20In-N-Out%20Animal-style%20burgers.%20I%20could%20not%20taste%20the%20onions%20at%20all.%20I'd%20rather%20have%20real%20onion%20slivers%20than%20dehydrated%2Frehydrated%20onions.%20The%20shredded%20lettuce%20on%20my%20Big%20Mac%20didn't%20look%20or%20taste%20any%20different.%20I%20didn't%20see%20any%20wilted%20pieces.%20The%20two%20pickles%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20did%20look%20bigger.%20One%20was%20oblong-shaped%20compared%20to%20the%20standard%20round%20pickles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECheese%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20is%20rolling%20out%20changes%20to%20elevate%20its%20burgers.%20We%20tried%20the%20improved%20burgers%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Ohio.%20%20A%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20new%20onion%20prep.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657102b50ec98e92f74cfbce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThat%20cheese%20is%20not%20melted.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcDonald's%20promised%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20''Perfectly%20melted%20cheese%20that%20will%20make%20you%20want%20to%20savor%20every%20last%20bit%20off%20the%20wrapper.%26quot%3B%20And%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20cheese%20is%20taken%20out%20of%20refrigerators%20ahead%20of%20time%20so%20it%20melts%20more%20easily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloria%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20was%20the%20biggest%20miss%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%20Melty%2C%20gooey%20cheese%20can%20cover%20a%20multitude%20of%20sins%20(like%20dry%20burgers).%20But%20my%20cheese%20was%20very%20much%20an%20unmelted%20square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENancy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20cheese%20was%20not%20perfectly%20melted%20as%20billed.%20It%20was%20unevenly%20melted.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20oversauced%20Big%20Mac%20caused%20the%20cheese%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20cheese%20spread%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20beef%20patty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBurgers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Big%20Mac%20with%20hole%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571f34058e7c0c29a2aa5e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20new%20Big%20Mac%20had%20two%20holes%20in%20the%20beef%20patty%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMcDonald's%20promised%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit%20was%20%26quot%3Badjusting%20our%20grill%20settings%20for%20a%20better%20sear.%26quot%3B%20They%20told%20the%20Journal%20it%20was%20cooking%20six%20burgers%20at%20a%20time%20instead%20of%20eight%20for%20improved%20consistency%2C%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Bcalibrated%20the%20gap%20on%20the%20metal%20clamshell%20that%20presses%20burgers%20on%20the%20grill%20down%20to%20the%20millimeter%2C%20to%20avoid%20pressing%20too%20hard%20and%20squeezing%20out%20all%20the%20juices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloria%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20had%20low%20expectations%20here%2C%20and%20the%20burger%20met%20them.%20It's%20hard%20to%20churn%20out%20as%20many%20burgers%20as%20McDonald's%20does%20and%20keep%20them%20juicy.%20It%20seems%20much%20easier%20to%20control%20things%20like%20toppings.%20I'm%20not%20over%20the%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENancy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20top%20patty%20had%20two%20very%20noticeable%20holes.%20Not%20a%20good%20first%20impression.%20Time%20to%20recalibrate%20the%20grill.%20These%20patties%20had%20no%20juice%20to%20them%2C%20but%20they%20still%20had%20a%20greasy%20aftertaste.%20Each%20Big%20Mac%20patty%20was%20paper%20thin.%20It%20looked%20like%20they%20were%20cooked%20in%20a%20vice.%20Maybe%20things%20will%20change%20soon.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-to-start-selling-bigger-burgers-menu-fast-food-restaurants-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Chris%20Kempczinski%20told%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20chain%20is%20looking%20into%20creating%20%26quot%3Ba%20larger%20burger.%26quot%3B%20It's%20unclear%20if%20he%20means%20a%20new%20bigger-size%20burger%20or%20bigger%20patties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConclusion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloria%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20theory%2C%20I%20understand%20wanting%20to%20make%20these%20small%20tweaks.%20People%20love%20McDonald's%20burgers%2C%20particularly%20the%20Big%20Mac%2C%20so%20they%20would%20be%20outraged%20by%20any%20significant%20change.%20But%20some%20of%20these%20tweaks%20don't%20seem%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20model%2C%20which%20values%20speed.%20One%20of%20the%20tweaks%2C%20having%20employees%20get%20lettuce%20and%20pickles%20from%20coolers%20more%20frequently%20for%20optimal%20freshness%2C%20seems%20like%20the%20opposite%20of%20efficiency.%20And%20as%20much%20as%20I%20want%20that%20perfectly%20melted%20cheese%2C%20how%20do%20you%20automate%20and%20streamline%20getting%20the%20cheese%20out%20of%20the%20fridge%20and%20onto%20the%20burger%20at%20just%20the%20right%20time%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20melts%20on%20the%20burger%3F%20I%20think%20McDonald's%20needs%20to%20rethink%20quite%20a%20few%20of%20these%20tweaks%20and%20consider%20how%20to%20scale%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENancy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20taken%20McDonald's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhospitality%2Fmcdonalds-burger-new-menu-2400d22b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseven%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20to%20revamp%20its%20dry%20burgers.%20For%20that%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20I%20expect%20a%20major%20transformation.%20I%20expected%20a%20burger%20that%20would%20dazzle%20me%20from%20the%20first%20bite.%20Little%20tweaks%20like%20the%20improved%20pickles%20and%20bun%20made%20the%20Big%20Mac%20present%20better.%20But%20it%20didn't%20taste%20better.%20I%20came%20in%20with%20high%20expectations%20and%20left%20with%20a%20greasy%2C%20not%20juicy%2C%20taste%20in%20my%20mouth.%20Maybe%20it's%20time%20to%20invent%20an%20entirely%20new%20burger%2C%20rather%20than%20spend%20seven%20years%20repairing%20burgers%20that%20can't%20be%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-updated-big-mac-reviewed-compared-against-promises-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702414177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578936a0ec98e92f74e8f4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-updated-big-mac-reviewed-compared-against-promises-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McDonald's%20announced%20tweaks%20to%20its%20burgers%2C%20including%20its%20Big%20Mac.%20We%20reviewed%20and%20evaluated%20the%20burger%20buns%2C%20cheese%2C%20condiments%2C%20and%20Mac%20sauce.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nluna%40insider.com%20(Nancy%20Luna%2CGloria%20Dawson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-updated-big-mac-reviewed-compared-against-promises-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20loses%20antitrust%20court%20battle%20with%20makers%20of%20Fortnite%20video%20game%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702413469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fph