ef%20Told%20New%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVisiting%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20or%20FBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20has%20assured%20India%20that%20the%20US%20is%20probing%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20San%20Francisco%20%26quot%3Baggressively%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20be%20able%20to%20share%20%26quot%3Bcredible%26quot%3B%20leads%20soon%2C%20sources%20said.%20Mr%20Wray%20met%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20Director%20Dinkar%20Gupta%20on%20second%20day%20of%20his%20visit%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Khalistan%20supporters%20attacked%20and%20damaged%20the%20Indian%20Consulate.%20It%20was%20again%20attacked%20in%20July.%20The%20NIA%20team%20had%20visited%20San%20Francisco%20in%20August%20and%20returned%20with%20some%20leads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20between%20the%20investigating%20agency%20chiefs%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Washington's%20allegations%20about%20an%20Indian%20link%20to%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20Sikh%20separatist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%2C%20India%20flagged%20how%20freedom%20of%20expression%20is%20being%20misused%2C%20NDTV%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NIA%20chief%20highlighted%20how%20the%20nexus%20between%20terrorist%20outfits%20and%20terrorist%20elements%20with%20members%20of%20organised%20criminal%20syndicates%20spreading%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailed%20discussions%20were%20also%20held%20between%20both%20agencies%20on%20how%20to%20share%20real%20time%20intelligence%2C%20so%20that%20informed%20decisions%20can%20be%20taken%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscussions%20were%20also%20held%20on%20several%20pending%20extraditions%2C%20including%20that%20of%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack%20co-conspirator%20Tahawwur%20Rana%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20senior%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan-origin%20Canadian%20businessman%20Rana%20is%20wanted%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack.%20He%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20NIA%20chief%20pointed%20out%20that%20threats%20in%20the%20cyber%20domain%20were%20increasing.%20Digital%20space%20was%20also%20being%20effectively%20exploited%20by%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%20for%20propagating%20radical%20views%20and%20recruitment%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20NIA%20was%20also%20seeing%20use%20of%20crytocurrency%20for%20terror%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20difficulties%20encountered%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20obtaining%20data%20from%20encryption%20Apps%20were%20also%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20noted%20that%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20newer%20technologies%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%2C%20tracing%2C%20tracking%20and%20investigating%20crypto%20transactions%20is%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20challenge%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20both%20agencies%20recognised%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20organised%20crime%20networks%2C%20terror%20related%20crimes%2C%20cyber-enabled%20terror%20attacks%2C%20ransomware%20threats%2C%20economic%20crimes%20and%20transnational%20terror%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702406700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7ltcp1as_fbi-chief-meet-nia_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleads-soon-on-india-consulate-attack-fbi-chief-christopher-wray-told-delhi-sources-4662505%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Visiting%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20or%20FBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20has%20assured%20India%20that%20the%20US%20is%20probing%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20San%20Fra