the%20British%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20(BBC)%20premises%20in%20India%20facing%20%26quot%3Bsurveys%26quot%3B%20by%20tax%20authorities%20and%20an%20ensuing%20investigation%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20over%20alleged%20FDI%20violations%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20establishment%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom%20Private%20Limited%20ensures%20the%20BBC%20and%20Collective%20Newsroom%20can%20meet%20their%20shared%20commitment%20to%20Indian%20audiences%20and%20cover%20stories%20on%20India%20that%20matter%20to%20global%20audiences.%20It%20is%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20Indian%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20BBC%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollective%20Newsroom%20has%20been%20established%20as%20an%20Indian%20company%2C%20wholly%20owned%20by%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20with%20four%20existing%20staff%20members%20leaving%20the%20BBC%20to%20lead%20Collective%20Newsroom.%20These%20senior%20leaders%20have%20a%20wealth%20of%20editorial%20and%20programme-making%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BBC%20will%20commission%20Collective%20Newsroom%20to%20produce%20its%20six%20Indian%20language%20services%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%20digital%20output%20and%20Indian%20YouTube%20channel%20in%20English%20for%20audiences%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAudiences%20in%20India%20can%20be%20assured%20that%20the%20BBC's%20Indian%20language%20services%20and%20unique%20range%20of%20quality%20output%20will%20inform%2C%20educate%20and%20entertain%20audiences%20across%20our%20diverse%20and%20highly%20engaged%20country%20under%20the%20agreement%20between%20the%20BBC%20and%20Collective%20Newsroom.%20We%20launch%20Collective%20Newsroom%20with%20big%20ambitions%20for%20audiences%20in%20India%20and%20beyond%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rupa%20Jha%2C%20Senior%20News%20Editor%2C%20BBC%20India%2C%20and%20founding%20shareholder%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20it%20has%20a%20long-held%20and%20deep-rooted%20place%20in%20India's%20media%20landscape%2C%20having%20first%20launched%20the%20Hindi%20language%20service%20in%201940.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20developed%20a%20range%20of%20BBC%20output%2C%20expanding%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20language%20services%20and%20growing%20audience%20figures%20from%20%26quot%3Bdecade-to-decade%20with%20its%20agenda-setting%20and%20high%20impact%20journalism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BBC's%20presence%20in%20India%20is%20steeped%20in%20a%20rich%20history%20that%20has%20always%20put%20audiences%20first%2C%20so%20we%20warmly%20welcome%20the%20formation%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom%20which%20continues%20that%20progression.%20The%20BBC%20will%20get%20first%20class%20content%20from%20Collective%20Newsroom%20that%20will%20be%20rooted%20in%20India%20and%20in%20line%20with%20the%20editorial%20standards%20audiences%20expect%20from%20the%20BBC%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jonathan%20Munro%2C%20Deputy%20CEO%2C%20BBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiliane%20Landor%2C%20Senior%20Controller%2C%20BBC%20News%20International%20Services%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20the%20BBC's%20critical%20strengths%20are%20its%20truly%20global%20output%20for%20audiences%20and%20our%20reputation%20as%20a%20trusted%20source%20of%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20committed%20to%20excellence%20in%20journalism%20for%20and%20from%20India%2C%20and%20this%20agreement%20ensures%20the%20continued%20production%20of%20independent%2C%20international%20and%20impartial%20journalism%20that%20the%20BBC%20News%20brand%20is%20renowned%20for%20in%20India%20and%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20Under%20the%20new%20arrangement%2C%20activity%20for%20BBC%20Monitoring%20and%20the%20BBC's%20English%20language%20newsgathering%20operation%20for%20global%20output%20will%20remain%20with%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20content%20is%20provided%20in%20six%20languages%20-%20BBC%20News%20Hindi%2C%20BBC%20News%20Marathi%2C%20BBC%20News%20Gujarati%2C%20BBC%20News%20Punjabi%2C%20BBC%20News%20Tamil%2C%20BBC%20News%20Telugu%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20English%2C%20to%2082%20million%20people%20around%20the%20country%20on%20average%20each%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20statistics%2C%20BBC%20News%20Hindi%20is%20the%20BBC's%20language%20service%20with%20the%20largest%20audience%20and%20in%202023%2C%20across%20all%20platforms%2C%20its%20weekly%20reach%20figure%20grew%2027%20per%20cent%20year-on-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20World%20Service%20claims%20a%20reach%20of%20318%20million%20people%20on%20average%20every%20week%20globally%20and%20operates%2042%20different%20language%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702404840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F58bcnv6_bbc-office_625x300_17_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-to-create-new-entity-to-comply-with-fdi-rules-4661490%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20BBC%20staff%20members%20on%20Tuesday%20announced%20plans%20to%20leave%20the%20organisation%20and%20form%20a%20new%20entity%20in%20India%20named%20Collective%20Newsroom%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20services%20%26quot%3Bas%20commissioned%20by%20the%20BBC%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20country's%20FDI%20laws.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-to-create-new-entity-to-comply-with-fdi-rules-4661490%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbbc-india-restructures-to-create-new-entity-to-comply-with-fdi-rule