nganer%20seat%2C%20but%20he%20is%20not%20from%20the%20area.%20He%20hails%20from%20Bharatpur%2C%20which%20has%20never%20really%20been%20a%20happy%20hunting%20ground%20for%20the%20party.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20won%20this%20seat%20in%20each%20of%20the%20last%20two%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20did%20hold%20it%20in%202008%20and%202013%20but%20those%20wins%20followed%20a%2036-year%20drought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanganer%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%C2%A0is%20a%20BJP%20stronghold%3B%20the%20party%20has%20held%20this%20seat%20since%202003%20and%20has%20won%20it%20in%20eight%20of%2010%20Assembly%20elections%20since%201977%2C%20when%20it%20was%20formed.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20each%20of%20the%20past%20three%20state%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20never%20won%20less%20than%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20this%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explains-why-bjp-picked-mohan-yadav-madhya-pradesh-chief-minister-vishnu-deo-sai-chhattisgarh-chief-minister-rajasthan-chief-minister-4659210%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP's%202024%20Gameplan%20Behind%20Hattrick%20Of%20Heartland%20Surprises%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20in%20his%20debut%20election%2C%20was%20fielded%20from%20a%20safe%20seat%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%2C%20with%20some%20suggesting%20his%20becoming%20Chief%20Minister%20may%20have%20been%20planned%20by%20the%20BJP%20from%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20becoming%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20been%20pitched%20as%20the%20BJP's%20good%20practice%20of%20rewarding%20hard%20workers.%20A%20grinning%20brother-in-law%2C%20Pramod%20Sharma%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see...%20BJP%20has%20given%20such%20a%20huge%20responsibility%20to%20an%20ordinary%20worker.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20BJP%20does...%20elevate%20ordinary%20workers%20to%20big%20posts.%20He%20will%20carry%20out%20his%20responsibility%20very%20well.%20We%20had%20not%20expected%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20is%20from%20the%20Brahmin%20community%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20about%20seven%20per%20cent%20of%20Rajasthan's%20population%20and%2C%20including%20those%20from%20neighbouring%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20form%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20upper%20class%2C%20or%20'general%20category'%2C%20voters%20that%20are%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20BJP's%20support%20in%20this%20part%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ERajasthan%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20named%20two%20deputies%20for%20Mr%20Sharma%20-%20picks%20that%2C%20alongside%20his%20own%2C%20underline%20the%20caste%2Fclass%20arithmetic%20foremost%20in%20the%20party's%20mind%20before%20next%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEx-Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20who%20quit%20Parliament%20after%20winning%20last%20month's%20poll%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20deputies.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20former%20Jaipur%20royal%20family%2C%20Ms%20Kumari%20fits%20multiple%20bills%20for%20the%20BJP%20-%20a%20Rajput%20face%20in%20a%20state%20that%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20community%2C%20and%20a%20woman.%20The%20other%20deputy%20is%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Dalit%20community%20that%20makes%20up%20over%2016%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20population%2C%20and%20whose%20elevation%20gives%20the%20BJP%20a%20positive%20campaign%20platform%20for%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702402080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Faptihtm_bhajanlal-sharma-last-row-ndtv_625x300_12_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-rajasthan-chief-minister-bhajan-lal-sharma-bjps-bhajanlal-sharma-from-third-row-right-to-rajasthan-chief-minister-4660425%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20on%20Tuesday%20unveiled%20first-time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20as%20the%20new%2