rmany%20once%20the%20Berlin%20government%20was%20overthrown.%20They%20also%20began%20stockpiling%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20the%20suspects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany-reichsb%25C3%25BCrger-conspirators-planned-new-army-for-coup%2Fa-64066794%5C%22%3Eplanned%20to%20set%20up%20280%20armed%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20Germany%20that%20would%20have%20been%20tasked%20with%20%E2%80%9Carresting%20and%20executing%E2%80%9D%20people%20after%20a%20coup.%C2%A0They%20planned%20to%20break%20into%20the%20Reichstag%20parliament%20building%20in%20Berlin%20armed%20and%20arrest%20members%20of%20the%20Bundestag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20made%20numerous%20concrete%20preparations%20for%20the%20coup%20and%20the%20subsequent%20securing%20of%20power.%C2%A0The%20%E2%80%9CCouncil%E2%80%9D%C2%A0was%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20central%20body%20of%20a%20transitional%20administration%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20cabinet%20of%20a%20regular%20government.%20Its%20job%20was%20to%20negotiate%20a%C2%A0new%20state%20order%20in%20Germany%20with%20the%20Allied%20victorious%20powers%20of%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20states%20of%20Saxony%2C%20Thuringia%2C%20and%20Baden-W%C3%BCrttemberg%2C%20concrete%20preparations%20had%20already%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20the%20cases%20would%20be%20heard%20at%20higher%20regional%20courts%20in%20Frankfurt%2C%20Munich%20and%20Stuttgart.%20The%20more%20prominent%20cases%20are%20set%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20Frankfurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20movement%20believe%20deep-state%20conspiracy%20theories%20that%20deny%20the%20existence%20of%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20post-World%20War%20II%20Federal%20Republic%20and%20reject%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20German%20government.%20They%20claim%20that%20the%201937%20borders%20of%20the%20German%20empire%20still%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20therefore%20convinced%20by%20various%20conspiracy%20myths%C2%A0for%20example%20that%20Germany%20is%20currently%20ruled%20by%20members%20of%20a%20so-called%20deep%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20believed%20they%20would%20be%20liberated%20by%20a%20secret%20alliance%20that%20would%20work%20with%20them%20and%20give%20them%20the%20signal%20for%20%E2%80%9CDay%20X%E2%80%9D%20when%20the%20coup%20would%20be%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-existent%20society%20was%20said%20to%20include%20governments%2C%20intelligence%20services%20and%20militaries%20of%20various%20states%2C%20including%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20and%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany-charges-27-suspects-over-reichsb%25C3%25BCrger-coup-plot%2Fa-67703212%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702399995000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12221838%2Fpexels-ingo-joseph-109629.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgermany-charges-27-suspects-over-reichsburger-coup-plot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%20are%20strongly%20suspected%20of%20membership%20of%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20as%20well%20as%20preparation%20of%20a%20treasonous%20undertaking%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20a%20statem