as%20a%20trap%20to%20lure%20CC-1%2C%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20government%20official%20who%20the%20US%20indictment%20says%20initiated%20the%20murder%20plot.%20He%20says%20CC-1%20was%20clearly%20inexperienced%2C%20untrained%20and%20%E2%80%9Csloppy%E2%80%9D.%20Dulat%20says%20CC-1%20%E2%80%9Cwalked%20into%20a%20trap%E2%80%9D%20that%20was%20set%20for%20him.%20CC-1%20%E2%80%9Cbragged%E2%80%9D%2C%20thus%20giving%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20an%20American%20agent%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20detail%20and%20information%2C%20the%20former%20R%26amp%3BAW%20head%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FXc2Yf5_Uc80%3Fsi%3DnoJYRcj7CmhZdbKZ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20and%20so%20far%20only%20interview%20done%20by%20someone%20who%20has%20spent%20his%20entire%20career%20in%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20and%20R%26amp%3BAW%20talking%20extensively%20and%20in%20detail%20about%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20Dulat%20says%20repeatedly%20that%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20the%20National%20Security%20Advisor%2C%20would%20have%2Fshould%20have%20known%20about%20what%20was%20happening%20but%20insisted%20that%20Doval%20would%20not%20be%20complicit.%20Dulat%20also%20clearly%20said%20that%20others%2C%20either%20%E2%80%9Clateral%E2%80%9D%20to%20Doval%20or%20above%20him%20might%20have%20also%20been%20in%20the%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20describes%20CC-1%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%E2%80%9D%20who%20earlier%20worked%20in%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20adds%20%E2%80%9CCC-1%20was%20employed%20at%20all%20times%20relevant%20to%20this%20indictment%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20resides%20in%20India%20and%20directed%20the%20assassination%20plot%20from%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDulat%20said%20the%20American%20government%20and%20the%20US%20system%20as%20a%20whole%20have%20taken%20this%20indictment%20and%20the%20details%20it%20reveals%20very%20seriously%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20key%20meeting%20would%20have%20been%20the%20one%20between%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20the%20US%20NSA%20Jake%20Sullivan%20in%20August.%20This%20meeting%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20happened%20in%20Jeddah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20Dulat%20repeatedly%20denied%20speculation%20and%20rumours%2C%20which%20are%20quite%20widespread%2C%20that%20CC-1%20might%20be%20the%20former%20head%20of%20R%26amp%3BAW%2C%20Samant%20Goel.%20However%2C%20Dulat%20said%20Doval%20must%2Fshould%20know%20who%20CC-1%20is%20and%20was%20pretty%20certain%20action%20has%20already%20been%20taken%20against%20him%20and%20he%20has%20been%20suitably%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20the%20Americans%20wanted%20to%20lure%20CC-1%20into%20a%20trap%2C%20he%20said%20this%20is%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20smelt%E2%80%9D%20something%20about%20him.%20Dulat%20said%20that%20clearly%2C%20the%20United%20States%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Administration%20knows%20a%20lot%20more%20about%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20he%20described%20as%20their%20agent%2C%20than%20the%20indictment%20reveals%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20could%20be%20some%20surprises%20in%20store%20for%20India%20when%20further%20details%20and%20information%20are%20revealed.%20Dulat%20also%20said%20the%20CIA%20and%2C%20possibly%2C%20the%20FBI%20know%20more%20than%20India%20has%20been%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sizeable%20part%20of%20the%20interview%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20on%20June%2018%2C%20hours%20after%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20in%20Canada%2C%20CC-1%20%E2%80%9Csent%20Gupta%20a%20video%20clip%20that%20shows%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20bloody%20body%20slumped%20in%20his%20vehicle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDulat%20agreed%20that%20this%20does%20raise%20questions%20about%20how%20and%20from%20whom%20CC-1%20received%20this%20video%20clip%2C%20hours%20after%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20and%20agreed%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpossibly%E2%80%9D%20a%20link%20between%20CC-1%20and%20either%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killers%20or%20people%20very%20close%20to%20them%20who%20would%20have%20sent%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDulat%20said%20that%20this%20matter%20would%20soon%20be%20resolved%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%20but%2C%20he%20added%2C%20the%20US%20will%20want%20its%20pound%20of%20flesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20although%20Dulat%20begins%20by%20suggesting%20that%20the%20details%20in%20the%20US%20indictment%20are%20%E2%80%9Ca%20nice%20work%20of%20fiction%E2%80%9D%2C%20everything%20he%20says%20thereafter%20in%20the%20interview%20suggests%20that%20he%20accepts%20the%20details%20as%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702396500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12211912%2FKT-12-Dec-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-ajit-doval-pannun-plot-as-dulat-karan-thapar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20A.S.%20Dulat%20discusses%20the%20US%20federal%20prosecutor's%20allegation%20that%20an%20'identified%20Indian%20government%20employee'%20directed%20the%20murder%20plot%20of%20a%20US%20citizen%20on%20American%20soil.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-ajit-doval-pannun-plot-as-dulat-karan-thapar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20To%20Invest%20%24100%20Billion%20In%20Green%20Energy%20Transition%20Over%2010%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20today%20released%20its%20half-yearly%20ESG%20compendium%2C%20showing%20significant%20progress%20in%20its%20decarbonisation%20pathway%20and%20its%20ambition%20to%20support%20the%20global%20net-zero%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%2C%20which%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20India's%20green%20energy%20transition%2C%20has%20set%20a%20target%20to%20become%20net-zero%20by%202050%20or%20earlier%20for%20five%20of%20its%20portfolio%20companies%20-%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%2C%20Adani%20Energy%20Solutions%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20%26amp%3B%20SEZ%2C%20ACC%2C%20and%20Ambuja%20Cements%20-%20the%20conglomerate%20which%20is%20also%20India's%20largest%20integrated%20infrastructure%20developer%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EESG%2C%20or%20environmental%2C%20social%20and%20governance%20parameters%20is%20used%20to%20screen%20investments%20based%20on%20corporate%20policies%20and%20to%20encourage%20companies%20to%20act%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20will%20invest%20%24100%20billion%20in%20green%20energy%20transition%20over%2010%20years.%20The%20Adani%20portfolio%20businesses%20have%20active%20strategy%20to%20decarbonise%2C%20pledge%20to%20plant%20100%20million%20trees%20by%202030%2C%20and%20undertake%20innovative%20pilot%20projects%2C%20including%20development%20of%20hydrogen%20fuel%20cell%20electric%20truck%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20embarking%20on%20developing%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20ambitious%20green%20hydrogen%20ecosystems%20supported%20by%20a%20fully%20integrated%20value%20chain%20on%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roadmap%20to%20the%20net-zero%20transition%20will%20need%20last-mile%20green%20hydrogen%20solutions.%20To%20make%20green%20hydrogen%20adoption%20feasible%2C%20Adani's%20track%20record%20in%20large-scale%20renewables%20and%20fully%20integrated%20manufacturing%20with%20end-to-end%20EPC%20(engineering%2C%20pr