et-zero%20by%202040.%20In%20the%20first%20half%20of%20FY24%2C%20it%20achieved%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20share%20of%20renewables%20in%20the%20total%20energy%20mix%2C%20reduced%20energy%20intensity%20by%2046%20per%20cent%2C%20energy%20emission%20by%2048%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20water%20consumption%20intensity%20by%2059%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%20Enterprises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Enterprises%20is%20building%20three%20giga-factories%20with%20a%20target%20to%20develop%2010%20GW%20solar%20panels%2C%2010%20GW%20wind%20turbines%2C%20and%205%20GW%20hydrogen%20electrolysers%20as%20part%20of%20its%20low-cost%20integrated%20green%20hydrogen%20project.%20For%20solar%20module%20manufacturing%2C%20the%20glass%20factory%20is%20completed%2C%20with%20work%20commencing%20on%20the%20ingot%20and%20wafer%20plant.%20In%20October%2C%20the%20company%20started%20production%20of%20India's%20largest%20wind%20turbine%20of%205.2%20MW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EESG%20Innovations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProactive%20experimentation%20with%20green%20hydrogen-based%20decarbonisation%20solutions%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20anticipation%20of%20wider%20adoption%20as%20costs%20come%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20reduced%20emission%20and%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20Adani%20Power%20partnered%20with%20IHI%20Corporation%20and%20Kowa%20company%20to%20explore%20ammonia%20co-firing%20at%20the%20Adani%20Power%20Mundra%20plant.%20The%20studies%20aim%20at%20initially%20de-carbonising%20Adani's%20coal-fired%20plants%2C%20but%20with%20a%20larger%20objective%20to%20implement%20the%20technology%20in%20other%20coal-fired%20plants%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20significant%20move%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20Ashok%20Leyland%20and%20Ballard%20Power%20to%20develop%20a%20hydrogen%20fuel%20cell%20electric%20truck%20(FCET)%20for%20mining%20logistics%20and%20transportation%2C%20which%20wi