%20Airport%20on%20November%204.%20He%C2%A0had%20no%20passport%20or%20visa%2C%20and%20officials%20also%20couldn't%20find%20him%20on%20the%20passenger%20list%20for%20any%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20questioned%2C%20Ochigava%20gave%20false%20and%20misleading%20information%20about%20his%20travel%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20including%20initially%20telling%20CBP%20that%20he%20left%20his%20passport%20on%20the%20airplane%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20affidavit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20flight%20crew%2C%20most%20of%20them%C2%A0noticed%20Mr%20Ochigava%20on%20the%20flight%2C%C2%A0saying%20that%20he%20wandered%20around%20the%20plane%20and%20kept%20changing%20his%20seat.%20He%C2%A0allegedly%20asked%20for%20two%20meals%20during%20each%20meal%20service%2C%20and%20at%20one%20point%20attempted%20to%20eat%20the%20chocolate%20that%20belonged%20to%20members%20of%20the%20cabin%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20officials%20searched%20his%20bag%2C%20they%20found%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20Russian%20and%20Israeli%20identification%20cards%2C%C2%A0but%20no%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Copenhagen%20Airport%20spokesperson%20told%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fnews-and-advice%2Fpassenger-flight-without-passport-visa-ticket-b2462551.html%5C%22%3E%C2%A0The%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20''%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20can%20see%20from%20our%20surveillance%20that%20he%20has%20entered%20without%20a%20valid%20ticket.%20Copenhagen%20Airport%20has%20provided%20photo%20and%20video%20material%20to%20the%20authorities%20who%20are%20investigating%20the%20case.%20We%20take%20the%20matter%20very%20seriously%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20work%20we%20continuously%20do%20to%20adjust%20and%20tighten%20our%20guidelines%20to%20improve%20security.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mysterious%20case%20is%20now%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20FBI.%20As%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Frussian-man-flies-europe-lax-without-passport-visa-ticket-reports%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20agent%20confirmed%20that%20the%20suspect%2C%20who%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20stowing%20away%20on%20an%20aircraft%2C%20is%20being%20held%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFBI%20Agent%20Caroline%20Walling%2C%20who%20filed%20the%20complaint%2C%20shared%20details%20from%20an%20interview%20with%20Ochigava%20on%20November%205.%C2%A0The%20suspect%20said%20he%20was%20confused%2C%20had%20not%20slept%20for%20three%20days%2C%20and%20couldn't%20remember%20how%20he%20boarded%20a%20plane%20without%20a%20ticket%2C%20boarding%20pass%2C%20or%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Ochigava%20had%20a%20Ph.%20D%20in%20economics%20and%20marketing.%20He%20last%20worked%20as%20an%20economist%20in%20Russia%20a%20long%20time%20ago.%20He%20claimed%20he%20had%20not%20been%20sleeping%20for%20three%20days%20and%20did%20not%20understand%20what%20was%20going%20on.%20Ochigava%20stated%20he%20might%20have%20had%20a%20plane%20ticket%20to%20come%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20he%20was%20not%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Walling%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20did%20not%20remember%20how%20he%20got%20on%20the%20plane%20in%20Copenhagen.%20He%20also%20would%20not%20explain%20how%20or%20when%20he%20got%20to%20Copenhagen%20or%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20there.%20When%20asked%20how%20he%20got%20through%20security%20in%20Copenhagen%2C%20Ochigava%20claimed%20he%20did%20not%20remember%20how%20he%20went%20through%20security%20without%20a%20ticket%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ochigava%20is%20being%20held%20at%20the%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%20in%20Downtown%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20court%20later%20this%20month.%20If%20convicted%2C%20Mr%20Ochigava%20could%20be%20imprisoned%20for%20up%20to%20five%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp