%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImpact%20investment%20company%20Omidyar%20Network%20India%20will%20leave%20the%20country%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20operating%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20an%20exclusive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyourstory.com%2F2023%2F12%2Fomidyar-network-india-to-shut-operations%5C%22%3Ereport%20by%20YourStory%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmidyar%20Network%20India%20will%20stop%20new%20investments%20and%20leave%20India%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20In%20the%20next%20two%20months%2C%20the%20board%20will%20evaluate%20its%20portfolio%20and%20existing%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20several%20months%20of%20deliberation%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20Omidyar%20Network%20India%20will%20stop%20making%20new%20investments%20and%20will%20completely%20transition%20out%20of%20the%20market%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20next%20two%20months%2C%20the%20board%20and%20leadership%20team%20will%20assess%20how%20best%20to%20manage%20the%20organization's%20portfolio%20while%20recognizing%20the%20long%20and%20trusted%20partnerships%20that%20the%20Omidyar%20Network%20India%20team%20has%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmidyar%20Network%20is%20a%20venture%20of%20the%20Omidyar%20group%20that%20has%20invested%20in%20media%2C%20digital%20society%2C%20education%2C%20emerging%20tech%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202022%2C%20the%20US-based%20Omidyar%20was%20among%2010%20non-profits%20accused%20of%20allegedly%20conspiring%20to%20illegally%20facilitate%20the%20registration%20and%20renewal%20of%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%20(FCRA)%20licences.%20FCRA%20is%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20to%20receive%20foreign%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmidyar%20was%20also%20placed%20on%20a%20watch%20list%20by%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20in%202021%20and%20all%20of%20its%20foreign%20donations%20were%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmidyar%20India%20Network%20on%20its%20website%20says%20it%20invests%20in%20bold%20entrepreneurs%20who%20help%20create%20a%20meaningful%20life%20for%20every%20Indian%2C%20especially%20the%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20Indians%20in%20low-income%20and%20lower-middle-income%20populations%2C%20ranging%20from%20the%20poorest%20among%20us%20to%20the%20existing%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20drive%20empowerment%20and%20impact%20at%20scale%2C%20we%20work%20with%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20private%2C%20non-profit%2C%20and%20public%20sectors%2C%20who%20are%20tackling%20India's%20hardest%20and%20most%20chronic%20problems%2C%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702394700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fcqknjf0o_omidyar-network_625x300_12_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimpact-investor-omidyar-network-to-leave-india-after-a-decade-of-ops-4661488%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Impact%20investment%20company%20Omidyar%20Network%20India%20will%20leave%20the%20country%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20operating%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20an%20exclusive%20report%20by%20YourStory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimpact-investor-omidyar-network-to-leave-india-after-a-decade-of-ops-4661488%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimpact-investor-omidyar-network-to-leave-india-after-a-decade-of-ops-4661488%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimpact-investor-omidyar-network-to-leave-india-after-a-decade-of-ops-4661488%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20mobile%20network%20Kyivstar%20hit%20by%20'cyber-attack'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702394155000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fne