%20such%20a%20situation%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbqOp34OHGr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbqOp34OHGr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Raghav%20Chadha%20(%40raghav_chadha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fraghav_chadha%2Fstatus%2F1734553414523355476%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20the%20bill%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20argued%20against%20this%20provision%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20end%20all%20balance%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20selection%20process.%20It%20has%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20change%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20ordered%20that%20a%20three-member%20panel%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20pick%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Election%20Commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20absence%20of%20a%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20single-largest%20Opposition%20party%20would%20be%20on%20the%20panel%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702389540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F7lt3unvo_raghav-chadha-rajya-sabha_625x300_04_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbilldozer-raghav-chadha-scoffs-at-changes-in-bill-to-appoint-top-poll-officials-4660914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Raghav%20Chadha%20launched%20a%20vociferous%20protest%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20against%20a%20controversial%20bill%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20top%20three%20election%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2