ices%20in%20six%20Indian%20languages%20%E2%80%93%20Hindi%2C%20Marathi%2C%20Gujarati%2C%20Punjabi%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Telugu%20%E2%80%93%20apart%20from%20those%20in%20English%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%2C%20will%20be%20commissioned%20by%20the%20BBC%20and%20produced%20by%20Collective%20Newsroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20establishment%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom%20Private%20Limited%20ensures%20the%20BBC%20and%20Collective%20Newsroom%20can%20meet%20their%20shared%20commitment%20to%20Indian%20audiences%20and%20cover%20stories%20on%20India%20that%20matter%20to%20global%20audiences.%20It%20is%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20Indian%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20imposed%20a%20cap%20of%2026%25%20FDI%20for%20digital%20news%20outfits%20operating%20in%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fmedia%2Fentertainment%2Fmedia%2Fbbc-world-india-to-rejig-shareholding-seeks-time-till-end-of-fy24-to-ensure-compliance-with-fdi-norm%2Farticleshow%2F105916147.cms%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2099.99%25%20of%20BBC%20World%20Service%20India%E2%80%99s%20shares%20are%20owned%20by%20its%20UK-based%20public%20broadcaster.%20The%20new%20company%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20operations%20in%20April%202024%2C%20when%20the%20next%20financial%20year%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20Indian%20citizens%20who%20are%20leaving%20the%20BBC%20to%20form%20and%20lead%20Collective%20Newsroom%20are%20Rupa%20Jha%2C%20Mukesh%20Sharma%2C%20Sanjoy%20Majumder%20and%20Sara%20Hassan.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20senior%20leaders%20have%20a%20wealth%20of%20editorial%20and%20programme-making%20experience.%20The%20BBC%20will%20commission%20Collective%20Newsroom%20to%20produce%20its%20six%20Indian%20language%20services%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%20digital%20output%20and%20Indian%20YouTube%20channel%20in%20English%20for%20audiences%20globally%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BBC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F12%2F12%2Fbbc-india-to-now-be-collective-newsroom-to-comply-with-fdi-norms%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Collective%20Newsroom%20is%20expected%20to%20absorb%20all%20of%20BBC%20India%E2%80%99s%20staff%20but%20the%20new%20company%20may%20move%20out%20of%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20Delhi%2C%20located%20in%20Hindustan%20Times%20House.%20The%20report%20adds%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20salary%20and%20terms%20of%20employment%20for%20the%20employees%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom%20will%20be%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20BBC%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupa%20Jha%2C%20who%20will%20lead%20the%20company%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CAudiences%20in%20India%20can%20be%20assured%20that%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20language%20services%20and%20unique%20range%20of%20quality%20output%20will%20inform%2C%20educate%20and%20entertain%20audiences%20across%20our%20diverse%20and%20highly%20engaged%20country%20under%20the%20agreement%20between%20the%20BBC%20and%20Collective%20Newsroom.%20We%20launch%20Collective%20Newsroom%20with%20big%20ambitions%20for%20audiences%20in%20India%20and%20beyond.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Munro%2C%20the%20deputy%20CEO%20of%20BBC%20News%20said%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20India%20is%20%E2%80%9Csteeped%20in%20a%20rich%20history%20that%20has%20always%20put%20audiences%20first%E2%80%9D%20and%20welcomed%20the%20formation%20of%20Collective%20Newsroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20BBC%20was%20raided%20by%20Indian%20income%20tax%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fincome-tax-officials-bbc%5C%22%3Ein%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20days%20after%20it%20aired%20a%20documentary%20about%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots.%20Though%20the%20documentary%20was%20never%20aired%20on%20Indian%20television%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20see%20that%20it%20is%20not%20available%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fmediacentre%2F2023%2Fbbc-staff-members-launch-new-company-to-serve-audiences-with-bbc-indian-language-services%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fmediacentre%2F2023%2Fbbc-staff-members-launch-new-company-to-serve-audiences-with-bbc-indian-language-services%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702475554976000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0bsD06T32HWnVoPOGsRK0N%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20its%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Chas%20a%20long-held%20and%20deep-rooted%20place%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20media%20landscape%2C%20having%20first%20launched%20the%20Hindi%20language%20service%20in%201940.%20Since%20then%20it%20has%20developed%20a%20range%20of%20BBC%20output%2C%20expanding%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20language%20services%20and%20growing%20audience%20figures%20from%20decade-to-decade%20with%20its%20agenda-setting%20and%20high%20impact%20journalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20lot%20is%20also%20unsaid.%20It%20decided%20to%20make%20India%20a%20production%20hub%20for%20its%20World%20Service%20programmes%2C%20significantly%20expanding%20them%20after%202005-06%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20startled%20long-time%20BBC%20watchers.%20They%20had%20been%20firm%20about%20retaining%20%E2%80%98editorial%20control%E2%80%99%20and%20this%20meant%20retaining%20their%20London%20headquarters%20as%20a%20base%20for%20productions.%20The%20reason%20given%20was%20that%20political%20environments%20in%20most%20countries%20were%20not%20to%20be%20trusted%20with%20the%20BBC%20being%20able%20to%20independently%20and%20seamlessly%20report.%20Only%20a%20few%20countries%20in%20North%20America%20and%20Europe%20were%20trusted%20as%20production%20hubs.%20A%20belief%20in%202005-06%20that%20India%20had%20arrived%20as%20a%20stable%20and%20safe%20place%20for%20independent%20journalism%20guided%20that%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20India%20is%20among%20the%20bottom%20twenty%20countries%20in%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%2C%20at%20161%20out%20of%20180.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702388695000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14174753%2F3177606923_c89adf0e31_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffdi-rules-bbc-india-services-new-company-collective-newsroom-private-limited%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20Indian%20BBC%20staffers%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0Rupa%20Jha%2C%20Mukesh%20Sharma%2C%20Sanjoy%20Majumder%20and%20Sara%20Hassan%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0have%20set%20up%20a%20new%20entity%20called%20'Collective%20Newsroom%20Private%20Limited'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ffdi-rules-bbc-india-services-new-company-collective-newsroom-private-limited%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Javed%20compares%20Agastya%20to%20Rishi%20Kapoor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702387890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105938540%2Cimgsize-60442.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjaved-akhtar-compares-agastya-nanda-to-rishi-kapoor-in-bobby-says-he-is-alternative-to-toxic-heroes%2Farticleshow%2F105938540.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105938540.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJaved%20Akhtar%20praises%20Amitabh%20Bachchan's%20grandson%20Agastya%20Nanda's%20Bollywood%20debut%20in%20'The%20Archies'.%20Farhan%20Akhtar%20hails%20Agastya%20as%20a%20brilliant%20