%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67691484.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Attempt%20To%20Smuggle%20Luxury%20Car%20Into%20North%20Korea%20Foiled%20By%20Japan%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20attempt%20to%20smuggle%20a%20%2470%2C000%20Lexus%20sedan%20into%20North%20Korea%20was%20foiled%20by%20the%20police%20in%20Japan%20last%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fweek-asia%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3244737%2Fnorth-koreas-attempts-smuggle-luxury-goods-expose-un-sanctions-regime-may-be-open-abuse%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20car%20was%20intercepted%20on%20the%20same%20day%20North%20Korea%20recalled%20its%20ambassador%20to%20Switzerland%20amid%20an%20investigation%20into%20ivory%20trafficking%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%20The%20car%20was%20seized%20during%20a%20raid%20on%20a%20used%20car%20showroom%20on%20December%207%20in%20Chiba%20prefecture.%20Japanese%20news%20outlet%20%3Cem%3EAsahi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20showroom%20had%20submitted%20papers%20stating%20that%20the%20luxury%20car%20was%20being%20sent%20to%20Singapore%20via%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owners%20of%20the%20showroom%20are%20being%20questioned%20and%20the%20police%20are%20looking%20at%20their%20previous%20transfers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seizure%20became%20news%20because%20exports%20of%20luxury%20cars%20and%20other%20high-end%20items%20to%20North%20Korea%20are%20banned%20under%20a%20UN%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20came%20into%20force%20in%202006%20when%20Pyongyang%20carried%20out%20underground%20nuclear%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENK%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20US-based%20North%20Korea-focused%20news%20outlet%20said%20that%20Kim%20Jong-Un%20is%20fond%20of%20luxury%20cars%20and%20has%20been%20previously%20seen%20in%20a%20Mercedes-Maybach%20GLS%20600%20and%20a%20Lexus%20LX%20SUV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20base%20price%20of%20the%20Mercedes-Maybach%20is%20around%20%24200%2C000%2C%20it%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20latest%20seizure%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fkim-jong-un-busted-trying-smuggle-luxury-lexus-north-korea-1851398%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewswee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ek%2C%20Anthony%20Ruggiero%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20non-proliferation%20and%20biodefense%20at%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Defense%20of%20Democracies%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20may%20not%20be%20Kim%20directly%2C%20but%20his%20people%20know%20what%20he%20likes%20and%20what%20the%20elites%20like.%20They%20import%20luxury%20goods%20using%20money%20earned%20via%20sanctions%20evasion%2C%20and%20they%20do%20not%20use%20that%20money%20for%20the%20North%20Korean%20people%20who%20are%20suffering%20under%20the%20Kim%20regime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuggiero%20further%20said%20that%20the%20Kim%20regime%20is%20able%20to%20circumvent%20US%20and%20UN%20sanctions%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20Washington%20is%20unwilling%20to%20sanction%20evaders%2C%20including%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20individuals%2C%20and%20banks%20that%20support%20North%20Korea's%20sanctions%20evasion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Han%20Tae-song%2C%20North%20Korea's%20ambassador%20to%20Switzerland%2C%20is%20being%20probed%20by%20UN%20Security%20Council%20Sanctions%20Committee%20over%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20smuggling%20poached%20ivory%20in%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHan%2C%20who%20has%20served%20as%20both%20North%20Korea's%20ambassador%20to%20Switzerland%20since%202017%20and%20its%20representative%20to%20the%20UN%20in%20Geneva%2C%20was%20also%20expelled%20from%20Zimbabwe%20in%201992%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20trafficking%20in%20rhino%20horn%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702387020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F2h7bemg8_kim-jong-un-train_625x