v%20Thackeray%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20any%20official%20information%20about%20such%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20anything%20official%20comes%20out%2C%20then%20that%20day%20we%20will%20reveal%20the%20information%20with%20us%20about%20them.%20If%20they%20level%20false%20allegations%20against%20us%2C%20then%20we%20will%20bring%20out%20the%20true%20information%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20said%20without%20naming%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fjk3pp2sg_disha-salian-650_625x300_18_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-team-to-probe-death-of-sushant-singh-rajputs-ex-manager-disha-salian-4660119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Police%20on%20Tuesday%20formed%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20to%20probe%20the%20death%20of%20Disha%20Salian%2C%20the%20ex-manager%20of%20late%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-team-to-probe-death-of-sushant-singh-rajputs-ex-manager-disha-salian-4660119%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-team-to-probe-death-of-sushant-singh-rajputs-ex-manager-disha-salian-4660119%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspecial-team-to-probe-death-of-sushant-singh-rajputs-ex-manager-disha-salian-4660119%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20named%20Rajasthan%20CM%3B%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%20Dy%20CMs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F12%2Ffull%2F1702378989-4231.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-elections%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-named-rajasthan-cm-diya-kumari-prem-chand-bairva-dy-cms-123121200770_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhajanlal%20Sharma%2C%2056%2C%20hails%20from%20Bharatpur%2C%20has%20been%20a%20long-time%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20party%20but%20this%20was%20his%20first%20run%20as%20MLA%20from%20the%20Sangner%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20which%20falls%20under%20the%20Jaipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20consti%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-elections%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-named-rajasthan-cm-diya-kumari-prem-chand-bairva-dy-cms-123121200770_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Frajasthan-elections%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-named-rajasthan-cm-diya-kumari-prem-chand-bairva-dy-cms-123121200770_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Felections%2Frajasthan-elections%2Fbhajanlal-sharma-named-rajasthan-cm-diya-kumari-prem-chand-bairva-dy-cms-123121200770_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Gripping%20Deep%20Dive%20Into%20the%202015%20FTII%20Students'%20Agitation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2Fftii-strikers.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20139%20days%20in%20mid-2015%2C%20students%20of%20the%20Film%20and%20Television%20Institute%20of%20India%20(FTII)%20were%20on%20strike%2C%20an%20action%20initially%20triggered%20by%20the%20appointment%20of%20an%20unworthy%20individual%20to%20the%20post%20of%20Chairman%20and%20a%20few%20more%20of%20even%20less%20distinction%20to%20the%20Governing%20Council.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20Ashish%20Rajadhyaksha%E2%80%99s%20one-of-a-kind%20volume%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EJohn-Ghatak-Tarkovsky%3A%20Citizens%2C%20Filmmakers%2C%20Hackers%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fairly%20comprehensive%2C%20non-linear%20chronicle%20of%20the%20strike.%20He%20brings%20to%20this%20task%20his%20intimate%20familiarity%20with%20the%20institution%2C%20its%20faculty%2C%20and%20its%20graduates%20from%20the%20earliest%20years%20of%20its%20existence%20to%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajadhyaksha%20presents%20conversations%20he%20has%20had%20with%20the%20principal%20protagonists%20of%20the%20strike%2C%20he%20cites%20from%20the%20films%20some%20of%20them%20made%20during%20the%20strike%20where%20they%20themselves%20and%20others%20spoke%20about%20their%20fears%2C%20expectations%2C%20their%20determination%20not%20to%20yield%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98carrots%E2%80%99%20being%20held%20out%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20book%2C%20the%20primary%20motivation%20for%20writing%20it%2C%20it%20is%20by%20no%20means%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20it.%20The%20whole%20thing%20is%20an%20intricate%20network%20of%20intersecting%20diachronic%20narratives%20and%20synchronic%20reportage%20encompassing%20the%20history%20of%20the%20FTII%20as%20an%20institution%20along%20with%20the%20nearby%20National%20Film%20Archive%20of%20India%20(NFAI)%2C%20the%20careers%20of%20FTII%20graduates%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20mainstream%20industry%2C%20the%20history%20of%20strikes%20at%20the%20FTII%2C%20the%20history%20of%20student%20strikes%20in%20general%20and%20especially%20the%20era%20of%20student%20actions%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20Jadavpur%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20the%20FTII%20strike%20was%20an%20early%20signal.%20Government%20policy%20measures%2C%20including%20committee%20reports%2C%20acts%20of%20parliament%2C%20censorship%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20an%20abiding%20concern%20of%20the%20author%20who%20has%20written%20extensively%20on%20these%20matters%20%E2%80%93%20prove%20salient%20to%20the%20many%20stories%20he%20interweaves%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161554%2Fdownload-12.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22351%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshish%20Rajadhyaksha%3Cbr%3EJohn-Ghatak-Tarkovsky%3A%20Citizens%2C%20Filmmakers%2C%20Hackers%3Cbr%3ESSAF-Tulika%20Books%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20a%20telling%20history%20of%20cancelled%20screenings%20that%20is%20as%20central%20to%20these%20stories%20as%20it%20is%20to%20the%20republic%E2%80%99s%20rapidly%20declining%20political%20health%3A%20these%20too%20are%20detailed%20and%20some%20of%20them%20are%2C%20in%20retrospect%2C%20the%20immediate%20risk%20to%20lives%20having%20passed%2C%20quite%20amusing%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Kirori%20Mal%20college%20screening%20of%20%3Cem%3EMuzaffarnagar%20Baqi%20Hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20once%20the%20clich%C3%A9%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20inappropriate%3A%20this%20is%20the%20product%20of%20a%20labour%20of%20love.%20It%20is%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20anyone%20other%20than%20Rajadhyaksha%20undertaking%20such%20a%20unique%20project.%20The%20established%20distinctions%20between%20film%20studies%2C%20film%20history%2C%20film%20appreciation%2C%20film%20education%20are%20blurred%2C%20the%20industry%2C%20mainly%20Mumbai%2C%20features%20alongside%20the%20parallel%20cinema%2C%20the%20passage%20from%20celluloid%20to%20digital%20is%20captured%20in%20its%20own%20right%2C%20as%20much%20as%20for%20the%20vital%20role%20it%20began%20to%20play%20in%20the%20latter%20part%20of%20the%20strike%20period%2C%20marking%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20way%20the%20author%20handled%20the%20subject%20in%20his%20previous%20book%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Cinema%20in%20the%20Time%20of%20Celluloid%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20engaging%20and%20instructive%20profiles%20of%20the%20principal%20protagonists%20of%20the%20strike%2C%20Naveen%20Padmanabha%2C%20Ranjit%20Nair%2C%20Harishankar%20Nachimuthu%2C%20Vikas%20Urs%2C%20Kshama%20Padalkar%2C%20Kislay%2C%20Prateek%20Vats%20and%20as%20well%20as%20others%20who%20were%20not%20centrally%20involved%20in%20the%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0some%20of%20them%20even%20unhappy%20with%20the%20turn%20of%20events%20%E2%80%93%20the%20films%20they%20made%2C%20the%20problems%20they%20faced%20as%20a%20strike%20team%20and%20as%20individuals.%20Older%20graduates%20or%20near%20graduates%20make%20their%20appearance%20too%3A%20Paresh%20Kamdar%2C%20Farida%20Mehta%2C%20but%20also%20Ritwik%20Ghatak%2C%20Kundan%20Shah%2C%20Sudhir%20Mishra%2C%20Girish%20Kasaravalli.%20Indeed%2C%20all%20of%20Chapter%203%2C%20with%20the%20making%20of%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Bhi%20Do%20Yaro%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20its%20centre%2C%20is%20a%20delightful%20read.%20Cameras%2C%20from%20the%20Mitchell%20to%20the%20latest%20digital%20offering%2C%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20strike%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20ecosystem%20has%20no%20place%20for%20close%20readings%20of%20films%2C%20Rajadhyaksha%20offers%20interesting%20takes%20on%20some%20of%20the%20graduates%E2%80%99%20films%2C%20notably%20Prateek%20Vats%E2%80%99%20%3Cem%3EEeb%20Allay%20Oo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2019)%2C%20seeing%20in%20them%20a%20commentary%20on%20the%20state%20of%20things%20at%20the%20institution%20as%20well%20as%20the%20country%20as%20a%20whole.%20There%20is%20a%20staggering%20wealth%20of%20detail%20in%20this%20work%20that%20can%20scarcely%20be%20summarised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20difficulties%20of%20writing%20about%20an%20event%20like%20the%20FTII%20strike%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20sufficiently%20distant%20in%20time.%20Thus%20the%20story%20is%20presented%20as%20a%20chronicle%2C%20though%20not%20without%20extensive%20commentary.%20This%20time%20is%20still%20with%20us%2C%20the%20struggles%20that%20broke%20out%20then%20continue%20to%20flare%20up%20in%20institutions%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20English%20and%20Foreign%20Languages%20University%20(EFLU)%20as%20I%20write%20this%2C%20students%20demanding%20action%20against%20sexual%20harassment%20have%20faced%20a%20hostile%20administration%2C%20while%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20assaulted%20by%20hooded%20men%20in%20the%20style%20of%20the%20JNU%20infiltration%20of%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20But%20it%20is%20still%20worth%20noting%20the%20three%20to%20four%20years%20during%20which%20multiple%20strikes%20and%20movements%20erupted%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20connecting%20and%20supporting%20one%20another%3A%20Jadavpur%20University%20(Hokkolorob)%2C%20Jamia%2C%20Hyderabad%20Central%20University%20(Rohith%20Vemula)%2C%20JNU%20Freedom%20Square%2C%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%2C%20then%20the%20anti-CAA%20movement%20and%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20which%20besieged%20Delhi%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20returning%20of%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20200px)%2085vw%2C%20200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161939%2F337528892_1155422449187054_7811838237578739008_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161939%2F337528892_1155422449187054_7811838237578739008_n.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12161939%2F337528892_1155422449187054_7811838237578739008_n-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAshish%20Rajadhyaksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20surprising%20is%20that%20one%20of%20the%20first%20of%20these%20was%20the%20FTII%20strike.%20From%20the%20history%20of%20student%20strikes%20in%20FTII%20traced%20in%20the%20book%20(chapter%202)%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20most%20of%20them%20were%20confined%20to%20matters%20of%20an%20intra-institutional%20nature.%20It%20is%20only%20in%202015%20that%20the%20strike%20acquired%20a%20wider%20significance%20of%20such%20magnitude%2C%20and%20became%20the%20harbinger%20of%20a%20season%20of%20struggles%20that%20have%20claimed%20many%20casualties%2C%20destroyed%20many%20futures%20but%20also%20stood%20as%20testament%20to%20the%20refusal%20to%20fall%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rajadhyaksha%20the%20FTII%20strike%2C%20and%20indeed%20all%20the%20other%20struggles%20discussed%2C%20exemplify%20the%20%E2%80%98networked%20protest%E2%80%99.%20The%20key%20word%20here%20is%20%3Cem%3Ehorizontalism%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20he%20puts%20it%3A%20%E2%80%98As%20the%20agitations%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20processions%20and%20occupy%20movements%2C%20they%20also%20brought%20into%20India%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20worldwide%20as%20the%20networked%20protest%2C%20and%20by%20a%20term%20originally%20coined%20in%20Argentina%20in%20December%202001%20as%20%3Cem%3Ehorizontalidad%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20horizontalism.%20Seeking%20to%20overcome%20the%20traditional%20hierarchies%20of%20organized%2C%20leader-driven%20political%20action%2C%20the%20effort%20to%20create%20new%20democratic%20social%20spaces%20was%20enabled%20by%20new%20technologies%20permitting%20horizontal%20peer-to-peer%20circulation%2C%20authorless%20memes%2C%20and%20the%20rapid%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20or%20what%20the%202019%20Hong%20Kong%20protestors%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98being%20water%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20of%20data%2C%20ideas%20and%20human%20action.%E2%80%99%20(p6)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tahrir%20Square%20demonstration%2C%20the%20Occupy%20movement%2C%20both%20of%20which%20date%20to%202011%20perhaps%20helped%20to%20spread%20this%20terminology.%20That%20vision%20of%20ultimate%20human%20autonomy%20where%20no%20one%20needs%20lead%20another%20along%20the%20right%20path%20or%20any%20path%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20is%20of%20course%20familiar%20to%20us%20from%20the%20socialist%20literature.%20It%20is%20the%20final%20goal%20of%20prophetic%20texts%2C%20even%20scientific%20ones%20such%20as%20those%20of%20Marx.%20What%20is%20new%20in%20the%20invocations%20of%20horizontality%20is%20the%20suggestion%20that%20such%20a%20state%20might%20already%20have%20been%20achieved.%20And%20yet%20the%20struggles%20continue.%20What%20are%20we%20to%20make%20of%20this%20paradox%3F%20This%20is%20not%20the%20place%20to%20go%20into%20a%20discussion%20of%20such%20matters.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20in%20celebrating%20horizontality%20serious%20theoretical%20questions%20may%20have%20been%20ignored.%20Consider%20the%20slogans%2C%20which%20are%20given%20their%20due%20place%20in%20Rajadhyaksha%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20one%20that%20serves%20as%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20title%3A%20John%20Ghatak%20Tarkovsky%20%E2%80%93%20We%20shall%20fight%20we%20shall%20win%3B%20Go%20back%20Chauhan%2C%20Ghatak%20was%20here!%3B%20Eisenstein%2C%20Pudovkin%20%E2%80%93%20We%20shall%20fight%20we%20shall%20win.%20Were%20there%20no%20leaders%20of%20the%20FTII%20strike%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20I%20must%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20book%20as%20artifact.%20I%20have%20seen%20nothing%20that%20even%20remotely%20resembles%20it.%20Photographs%20in%20a%20book%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20plenty%20here%2C%20are%20nothing%20new.%20Nor%20is%20the%20inclusion%20of%20reproductions%20of%20archival%20documents%2C%20which%20fill%20many%20pages%20of%20this%20volume.%20(My%20favourite%20is%20a%20handwritten%20%E2%80%98chart%20of%20the%20genesis%20of%20FTII%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20pioneer%20of%20film%20appreciation%2C%20Satish%20Bahadur).%20What%20is%20new%20are%20the%20number%20of%20QR%20codes%20which%20take%20you%20to%20more%20documents%2C%20articles%2C%20reports%20and%20books%20easily%20amounting%20to%20a%20few%20thousand%20pages.%20Is%20it%20a%20book%3F%20Is%20it%20an%20archive%3F%20Is%20it%20an%20art%20installation%3F%20Hard%20to%20say%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20gripping%20documentation%20of%20an%20important%20moment%20in%20recent%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.%20Madhava%20Prasad%20is%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Cultural%20Studies%2C%20The%20English%20and%20Foreign%20Languages%20University%2C%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2Fftii-strikers.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-gripping-deep-dive-into-the-2015-ftii-students-agitation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ashish%20Rajadhyaksha%E2%80%99s%20one-of-a-kind%20volume%20%E2%80%93%20John-Ghatak-Tarkovsky%3A%20Citizens%2C%20Filmmakers%2C%20Hackers%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20fairly%20comprehensive%2C%20non-linear%20chronicle%20of%20the%20strike.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-gripping-deep-dive-into-the-2015-ftii-students-agitation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mohan%20Yadav%3A%20Little%20Known%20Outside%20Ujjain%2C%20BJP's%20CM%20Pick%20for%20MP%20Baffles%20Party%20Leaders%2C%20Cadres%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12170059%2FEffect-27.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Like%20everyone%20present%20in%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20newly%20elected%20163%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MLAs%20on%20December%2011%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20was%20stunned%20when%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20election%20observer%20and%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20announced%20that%20three-time%20lawmaker%20from%20the%20Ujjain%20(South)%20seat%20is%20the%20party%20high%20command%E2%80%99s%20choice%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20was%20seated%20in%20the%20third%20row%20in%20the%20meeting%20when%20the%20announcement%20was%20made.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20utterly%20surprised%20to%20hear%20that%20the%20party%20has%20given%20such%20a%20big%20responsibility%20to%20a%20small%20worker%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20told%20the%20media%20after%20the%20meeting.%20It%20took%20a%20while%20for%20the%20import%20of%20the%20news%20to%20sink%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBafflement%20over%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-pervasive%20bafflement%20in%20the%20meeting%20was%20understandable.%20For%2C%20none%20of%20those%20present%20had%20the%20foggiest%20of%20idea%20that%20the%20party%20high%20command%20would%20prefer%20a%20district-level%20leader%20over%20an%20impressive%20array%20of%20claimants%20for%20the%20post%20who%20have%20spent%20decades%20carving%20out%20a%20niche%20for%20themselves%20in%20state%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20outgoing%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20had%20prior%20information%20about%20the%20sensational%20development.%20Khattar%20had%20told%20Chouhan%20to%20propose%20the%20name%20of%20Mohan%20Yadav%20in%20their%20meeting%20half%20an%20hour%20ahead%20of%20the%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20high%20command%E2%80%99s%20diktat.%20With%20a%20heavy%20heart%2C%20Chouhan%20followed%20the%20order%20even%20as%20half%20a%20dozen%20claimants%20such%20as%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20and%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%20gloomily%20looked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGloom%2C%20surprise%2C%20and%20suspense%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20while%20later%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20Tomar%20got%20a%20consolation%20prize%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20post%20of%20assembly%20speaker.%20But%20the%20other%20probables%20remained%20unlucky.%20Their%20disappointment%20deepened%20when%20it%20transpired%20in%20the%20meeting%20that%20the%20high%20command%20had%20deprived%20them%20of%20the%20post%20of%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20as%20well.%20For%20the%20two%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20posts%2C%20the%20names%20of%20Jagdish%20Devra%20(a%20Dalit)%20and%20Rajendra%20Shukla%20(a%20Brahmin)%20were%20announced%20in%20the%20meeting%20itself.%20The%20episode%2C%20marked%20by%20gloom%2C%20surprise%2C%20and%20suspense%2C%20lasted%2045%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20news%20of%20Yadav%20having%20been%20picked%20up%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20big%20shoes%20of%20Chouhan%20spread%20everyone%20was%20stunned.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20are%20known%20for%20their%20penchant%20for%20springing%20surprises.%20But%20nobody%20had%20imagined%20that%20the%20element%20of%20surprise%20would%20stretch%20this%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2FModi-Shah.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20president%20Amit%20Shah%20at%20the%20party's%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20meeting%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Delhi.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%2FBJP4Gujarat%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-199162%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22613%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20president%20Amit%20Shah%20at%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20meeting%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Delhi.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%2FBJP4Gujarat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20streets%2C%20in%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20in%20parks%2C%20on%20social%20and%20electronic%20media%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20spotted%20wrapping%20their%20heads%20around%20the%20big%20mystery%20as%20to%20what%20is%20so%20special%20in%20Yadav%20that%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20chose%20him%20for%20the%20hotly%20contested%20post%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-bjp-names-mohan-yadav-an-obc-leader-with-rss-roots-as-the-next-cm%5C%22%3EMP%3A%20BJP%20Names%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20an%20OBC%20Leader%20with%20RSS%20Roots%2C%20as%20the%20Next%20CM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%20is%20common%20knowledge%20among%20MLAs%20that%20Yadav%20is%20considered%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20His%20sharp%20rhetoric%20about%20Hindutva%20is%20also%20not%20a%20secret.%20But%20in%20a%20party%20where%20pouring%20scorns%20against%20Muslims%20has%20become%20par%20for%20the%20course%2C%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20extreme%20views%20are%20not%20considered%20high%20enough%20qualification%20for%20the%20top%20job.%20Nor%20does%20his%20hailing%20from%20the%20Yadav%20community%20set%20him%20apart%20in%20a%20party%20in%20which%2047%20MLAs%20belong%20to%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20reality%20check%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20media%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20has%20been%20describing%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20selection%20as%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20master%20stroke.%20However%2C%20the%20reality%20check%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suggest%20so.%20The%20election%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mark%20a%20generational%20transition%20if%20this%20is%20what%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20the%20world%20to%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2058%2C%20Yadav%20cannot%20be%20called%20young.%20Nor%20is%20he%20a%20face%20of%20generational%20change.%20His%20predecessor%20Chouhan%20is%20only%20six%20years%20older%20than%20Yadav.%20Chouhan%20was%2046%20years%20old%20when%20he%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20November%202005.%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20predecessor%20Uma%20Bharti%20was%20even%20younger%20(44)%20when%20she%20led%20the%20BJP%20to%20a%20spectacular%20victory%20in%202003.%20Also%2C%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20educational%20qualifications%20%E2%80%93%20Ph.D%2C%20MBA%2C%20LLB%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20make%20him%20a%20unique%20scholar%20among%20the%20MLAs%20given%20his%20antecedents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYadav%E2%80%99s%20political%20trajectory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20parameter%20of%20organisational%20and%20parliamentary%20experience%20too%2C%20Yadav%20is%20no%20match%20to%20either%20Chouhan%20or%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20his%20predecessors%20both%20of%20whom%20hailed%20from%20the%20OBC%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20assuming%20the%20office%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Chouhan%20had%20been%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20five%20times%20between%201991%20and%202005.%20In%20this%20period%2C%20he%20rose%20in%20the%20organisational%20ladder%20from%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Yuva%20Morcha%20(BJYM)%20to%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20and%20state%20party%20chief.%20Uma%20Bharti%20had%20been%20a%20five-time%20MP%20and%20Union%20cabinet%20minister%20before%20she%20became%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Anyway%2C%20she%20was%20already%20a%20national%20leader%2C%20thanks%20to%20her%20role%20in%20the%20Ramjanambhoomi%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20student%20and%20youth%20wings%20have%20been%20largely%20confined%20to%20the%20Ujjain%20district.%20His%20rise%20began%20with%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP).%20In%201982%2C%20he%20became%20the%20co-secretary%20of%20the%20student%20union%20of%20the%20Madhav%20Science%20College%20and%20became%20its%20president%20in%201984.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20he%20took%20charge%20as%20the%20city%20minister%20of%20the%20ABVP%20in%20Ujjain%20and%20became%20the%20department%20head%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201988%2C%20he%20was%20the%20co-minister%20of%20the%20ABVP%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20unit%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20national%20executive.%20In%201989-90%2C%20he%20became%20the%20minister%20of%20the%20ABVP%2C%20and%20in%201991-92%2C%20its%20national%20minister.%20In%201993-95%2C%20he%20was%20the%20co-area%20in-charge%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20Ujjain%20city%2C%20while%20in%201997%2C%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20Yuva%20Morcha%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20working%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20he%20was%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20BJP%20Yuva%20Morcha%E2%80%99s%20Ujjain%20division.%20Between%202000%20and%202003%2C%20he%20was%20the%20Ujjain%20district%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20in%202004%2C%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20working%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202004%20and%202010%2C%20he%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Ujjain%20Development%20Authority%20(with%20the%20rank%20of%20state%20minister).%20During%202011-2013%2C%20he%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20State%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20Bhopal%20(with%20the%20rank%20of%20cabinet%20minister).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20working%20committee.%20During%202013-2016%2C%20he%20was%20the%20co-convener%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Sanskritik%20Prakoshth%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20became%20an%20MLA%20in%202013%20from%20the%20Ujjain%20South%20seat%20and%20was%20elected%20again%20from%20the%20same%20seat%20in%202018%20and%202023.%20Yadav%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20as%20cabinet%20minister%20for%20higher%20education%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20political%20trajectory%20only%20barely%20touched%20the%20state%20level.%20Outside%20Ujjain%2C%20and%20possibly%20Malwa%20region%2C%20Yadav%20was%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20a%20pan-MP%20leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20Uma%20Bharti%20and%20Chouhan%20who%20have%20pan-Madhya%20Pradesh%20following%2C%20especially%20among%20OBCs%2C%20Yadav%20was%20never%20known%20to%20have%20any%20significant%20sway%20over%20these%20intermediary%20castes%20beyond%20Ujjain.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20associated%20at%20the%20state%20level%20with%20any%20Yadav%20caste%20outfits%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20defies%20comprehension%20as%20to%20how%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20will%20favourably%20impact%20the%20OBC%20vote%20banks%20in%20the%20Yadav-dominated%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaste%20dynamics%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20different%20from%20the%20two%20big%20northern%20states.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20Yadavs%20account%20for%2012%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20subsumed%20OBC%20identities%20under%20its%20Hindutva%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20is%20not%20the%20first%20chief%20minister%20in%20MP%20from%20the%20caste.%20Before%20him%2C%20Babulal%20Gaur%2C%20a%20Yadav%2C%20was%20in%20the%20post%20for%2015%20months%20in%202004-2005.%20He%20was%20unceremoniously%20ousted%20from%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20rich%20businessman%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20narrative%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20mounted%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20favoured%20media%20around%20Yadav%20is%20that%20the%20party%20has%20chosen%20a%20backward%20MLA%20from%20a%20humble%20background.%20Yadav%20was%20born%20in%20a%20small%20farmer%20family.%20His%20father%20ran%20a%20tea%20shop.%20But%2C%20today%2C%20he%20is%20a%20successful%20businessman%20with%20a%20considerable%20stake%20in%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20assets%20witnessed%20an%20exponential%20growth%20from%20Rs%2016%20crore%20(2013)%20to%2042%20crore%20in%2010%20years%20of%20his%20being%20an%20MLA%20and%20minister.%20In%20the%20affidavit%20he%20submitted%20for%20the%202018%20assembly%20election%2C%20Yadav%20declared%20his%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2031%20crore.%20The%20assets%20include%20land%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20love%20for%20acquiring%20land%20landed%20Yadav%20in%20a%20controversy%20in%20July%20this%20year.%20It%20was%20alleged%20that%20at%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20instance%2C%20the%20Ujjain%20administration%20changed%20the%20status%20of%2050%20out%20148%20hectares%20of%20land%20that%20was%20reserved%20for%20Simhastha%2C%20the%20regional%20congregation%20held%20every%2012%20years%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20from%20agricultural%20to%20residential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%2050-hectare%20land%20is%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Yadav%20and%20his%20kin.%20The%20Congress%20party%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move.%20It%20accused%20Yadav%20of%20trying%20to%20pressurise%20the%20administration%20to%20earn%20huge%20profits%20from%20the%20change%20in%20land%20use.%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Ujjain%20Paras%20Jain%20also%20joined%20the%20protest.%20In%20a%20core%20committee%20meeting%20in%20Ujjain%20over%20the%20master%20plan%2C%20Jain%20and%20Yadav%20had%20a%20strong%20altercation%20over%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20row%20snowballed%20in%20the%20media%2C%20outgoing%20CM%20Chouhan%20intervened%20and%20ordered%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20status%20of%20the%20disputed%20land%20as%20agricultural%20from%20residential.%20The%20urban%20development%20department%20soon%20followed%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20much%20to%20the%20annoyance%20of%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20not%20the%20only%20controversy%20Yadav%20got%20embroiled%20in.%20He%20was%20barred%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20from%20campaigning%20in%20the%20state%20by-polls%20for%20a%20day%20on%20October%2031%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20reprimanded%20him%20for%20using%20%E2%80%9Cintemperate%20language%20transgressing%20the%20limits%20of%20decency%E2%80%9D.%20Twenty-eight%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20gone%20for%20bypolls%20on%20November%203%2C%202020%2C%20following%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20after%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20and%20his%20loyalist%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20an%20election%20meeting%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20Yadav%20threatened%20the%20Congress%20with%20dire%20consequences%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20good%20for%20good%20people%20and%20bad%20for%20bad%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20someone%20wrongs%20us%2C%20we%20will%20bury%20such%20people%20under%20the%20earth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20seen%20threatening%20in%20a%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20kicked%20up%20another%20controversy%20during%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election.%20A%20video%20went%20viral%20showing%20him%20using%20extremely%20foul%20language%20against%20party%20workers%20scuffling%20with%20him.%20The%20video%20was%20again%20in%20circulation%20on%20social%20media%20after%20he%20was%20elected%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP%20legislature%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunally%20sensitive%20Ujjain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUjjain%2C%20from%20where%20Yadav%20hails%2C%20is%20known%20as%20a%20highly%20communally%20sensitive%20district.%20Communal%20tension%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20often%20flares%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20CM-designate%20has%20thrived%20financially%20and%20politically%20by%20mouthing%20provocative%20language%20against%20Muslims.%20His%20strong%20pro-Hindutva%20stance%20brought%20him%20close%20to%20the%20Sangh.%20The%20RSS%20is%20said%20to%20have%20a%20major%20say%20in%20his%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702382180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12170059%2FEffect-27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20choice%20of%20the%2058-year-old%20OBC%20leader%20by%20the%20party%20leadership%20has%20defied%20all%20comprehension%20given%20that%20the%20other%20claimants%20for%20the%20coveted%20post%20have%20more%20experience%20and%20popularity.%20Is%20Yadav's%20elevation%20a%20master%20stroke%20as%20is%20being%20described%20by%20the%20media%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MK%20Strinda%3A%20Yemen's%20rebel%20Houthis%20hit%20Norwegian%20tanker%20with%20missile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702381147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16290%2Fproduction%2F_131986709_mediaitem131986708.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67691216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Houthis%20have%20vowed%20to%20stop%20ships%20heading%20to%20Israel%2C%20but%20its%20owners%20say%20it%20was%20going%20to%20Italy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67691216%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67691216.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67691216.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP28%20stage%20stormed%20by%2012-year-old%20Indian%20activist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702380801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7EC0%2Fproduction%2F_131984423_p0gz2qqz.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-67691536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20girl%20held%20up%20a%20sign%20saying%20%26quot%3BEnd%20fossil%20fuel%2C%20save%20our%20planet%20and%20our%20future%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A122%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-67691536%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkey%20referee%20punched%3A%20Ankaragucu%20president%20Faruk%20Koca%20arrested%20after%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702380772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Flive-experience%2Fcps%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F736C%2Fproduction%2F_131984592_gettyimages-1841161602.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F67691038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Turkish%20football%20club%20president%20is%20arrested%20after%20punching%20a%20referee%20following%20a%20top-flight%20game%20on%20Monday%2C%20as%20all%20league%20football%20in%20the%20country%20is%20suspended.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A227%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F67691038%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F67691038.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F67691038.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP%3A%20Protecting%20the%20Lifestyle%20of%20the%20Well-Off%20For%20the%2028th%26nbsp%3BTime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12153224%2Fmike-marrah-x4QaRXytmow-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EReports%20are%20that%20in%202023%2C%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20the%20global%20temperature%20has%20been%20higher%20than%202%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20the%20pre-industrial%20level.%20This%20level%20of%20warming%20has%20been%20flagged%20as%20causing%20irreversible%20change.%20Already%20at%20the%20current%20average%20annual%20temperature%20level%20of%20about%201.3%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels%2C%20the%20number%20of%20extreme%20weather%20events%20has%20dramatically%20increased%2C%20resulting%20in%20growing%20distress%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOP28%20needed%20to%20plan%20for%20reversal%20of%20average%20global%20temperature%20from%20its%20current%20levels.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20on%20the%20agenda.%20A%20mitigation%20fund%20with%20paltry%20contributions%20has%20been%20proposed.%20The%20steps%20being%20discussed%20and%20the%20urgency%20required%20to%20reverse%20the%20rising%20average%20temperatures%20are%20not%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20today%20is%20not%20just%20global%20warming%20but%20the%20multi-faceted%20environmental%20pollution.%20Oceans%20and%20fresh%20water%20bodies%20are%20being%20severely%20polluted.%20There%20is%20impact%20on%20marine%20life%20and%20contaminants%20(like%20micro-plastics%20and%20chemicals)%20are%20entering%20human%20food%20chains.%20Heavy%20chemicals%20and%20elements%20are%20damaging%20various%20human%20organs%20with%20consequences%20for%20human%20health%20and%20leading%20to%20the%20proliferation%20of%20diseases%20like%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProduction%2C%20consumption%20and%20pollution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergy%20is%20required%20for%20the%20production%20of%20goods%20and%20services%2C%20their%20distribution%20and%20finally%20for%20consumption.%20Different%20forms%20of%20energy%20are%20available%20like%20electricity%2C%20wind%20power%2C%20burning%20coal%2C%20gas%20and%20petroleum%20products.%20Some%20are%20more%20polluting%20than%20others.%20For%20instance%2C%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20coal%20and%20diesel%20pollutes%20more%20than%20wind%20power%20or%20electricity%20from%20solar%20panels.%20Solar%20panels%20directly%20convert%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20rays%20into%20electricity%20while%20wind%20and%20hydro-electricity%20come%20indirectly%20from%20solar%20energy.%20These%20sources%20directly%20produce%20little%20or%20no%20greenhouse%20gases.%20However%2C%20production%20and%20setting%20up%20of%20solar%20panels%20and%20wind%20turbines%20also%20results%20in%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFossil%20fuels%20are%20stored%20green%20matter%20over%20millions%20of%20years%20and%20their%20burning%20produces%20greenhouse%20gases.%20Since%20they%20are%20easily%20available%2C%20their%20consumption%20has%20risen%20dramatically%20over%20time%20and%20that%20is%20leading%20to%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20greenhouse%20gases%20in%20air%20and%20global%20warming.%20So%2C%20one%20is%20talking%20of%20what%20is%20less%20polluting%20and%20which%20releases%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20greenhouse%20gases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20there%20are%20two%20problems.%20First%2C%20most%20of%20the%20energy%20is%20being%20derived%20from%20the%20wrong%20kind%20of%20sources%2C%20which%20pollute%20more%20than%20others%20and%20produce%20more%20greenhouse%20gases.%20Second%2C%20consumption%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20so%20more%20energy%20is%20required.%20Consumption%20is%20of%20all%20kind%20of%20goods%20and%20services.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20produced%2C%20transported%2C%20distributed%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20which%20requires%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20as%20production%20becomes%20more%20concentrated%2C%20there%20may%20be%20economies%20of%20scale%20but%20more%20transportation%20and%20distribution%20are%20required.%20It%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20long%20supply%20chains%20and%20distribution%20networks.%20So%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20greater%20efficiency%20due%20to%20use%20of%20more%20energy%20efficient%20methods%20of%20production%20and%20transportation%2C%20overall%20energy%20consumption%20has%20continued%20to%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEssential%20and%20luxury%20consumption%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProduction%20and%20distribution%20is%20related%20to%20consumption%20by%20humans%20for%20improvement%20in%20their%20welfare.%20A%20part%20of%20the%20output%20is%20for%20investment%2C%20to%20enable%20production%20to%20both%20continue%20and%20increase.%20Another%20part%20of%20consumption%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20public%20goods%20which%20are%20jointly%20consumed%2C%20like%20army%2C%20parks%2C%20sewage%20and%20public%20health.%20So%2C%20to%20address%20the%20problem%20of%20pollution%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20address%20private%20consumption%2C%20government%20consumption%20and%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20may%20also%20be%20characterised%20as%20essential%20and%20inessential.%20Food%2C%20water%2C%20clothing%20and%20housing%20are%20essential%20for%20life.%20Agriculture%20and%20livestock%20rearing%20which%20produce%20food%20are%20blamed%20for%20much%20of%20release%20of%20greenhouse%20gases.%20Apart%20from%20curbing%20waste%20in%20production%20of%20food%2C%20nothing%20much%20can%20be%20done%20about%20it.%20Public%20services%20are%20required%20for%20a%20civilised%20existence%20of%20citizens%2C%20so%20here%20too%20one%20can%20try%20to%20provide%20these%20more%20efficiently%20but%20these%20are%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20be%20curbed%20is%20inessential%20and%20luxury%20consumption.%20This%20has%20become%20huge%20amongst%20the%20well-off%2C%20government%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20corporate%20sector%2C%20and%20can%20be%20curtailed%20to%20reduce%20pollution.%20Unfortunately%2C%20consumption%20has%20become%20the%20yardstick%20of%20standard%20of%20living.%20Vacations%2C%20eating%20out%2C%20travel%2C%20throwing%20away%20usable%20things%2C%20discarding%20rather%20than%20repairing%20gadgets%2C%20etc.%2C%20have%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20well-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20demonstration%20effect%20from%20rich%20countries%2C%20the%20well-off%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20have%20copied%20wasteful%20consumption.%20The%20poor%20and%20the%20middle%20classes%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20try%20to%20emulate%20these%20consumption%20patterns.%20Advertising%20is%20used%20by%20producers%20to%20induce%20more%20consumption%2C%20not%20only%20among%20the%20well-off%20but%20among%20the%20less%20well-off%20and%20the%20poor.%20They%20are%20euphemistically%20defined%20as%20aspirational%20or%20those%20who%20want%20to%20consume%20more%20and%20can%20be%20induced%20to%20consume%20more%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumerism%20has%20become%20ingrained%20in%20life.%20It%20stands%20for%20consumption%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20consumption.%20Tremendous%20amount%20of%20waste%20is%20generated%20in%20producing%20and%20throwing%20away%20things%20or%20in%20fancy%20packaging%2C%20luxury%20five%20star%20living%2C%20etc.%20The%20poor%20are%20not%20a%20part%20of%20such%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkewed%20consumption%20pattern%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20who%20is%20consuming%20how%20much%20and%20therefore%20responsible%20for%20how%20much%20of%20the%20pollution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20socio-economic%20survey%20of%202018%20can%20be%20used%20to%20get%20the%20approximate%20consumption%20pattern.%20Translated%20to%20the%20all-India%20level%2C%20it%20suggests%20that%2090%25%20of%20Indian%20families%20spent%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month.%20So%2C%20about%20120%20crore%20Indians%20consumed%20less%20than%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20month.%20This%20gives%20an%20annual%20consumption%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%2028.8%20lakh%20crore.%2098%25%20of%20the%20families%20consumed%20less%20than%20Rs%2020%2C000%20per%20month.%20Assuming%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20month%20of%20family%20expenditure%20for%20those%20between%20the%2090%25%20and%2098%25%2C%20each%20individual%20in%20this%20bracket%20was%20consuming%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20month.%20Their%20consumption%20would%20be%20Rs%203.8%20lakh%20crore.%20This%2098%25%20has%20little%20spare%20resources%20to%20waste%20or%20spend%20on%20luxury%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%202%25%20of%20the%20families%20in%20India%20were%20rich%20and%20consumed%20the%20maximum.%20In%202018-19%2C%20national%20income%20was%20about%20Rs%20167%20lakh%20crore.%20Of%20this%20about%2058%25%20was%20private%20consumption%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2096.9%20lakh%20crore.%20Subtracting%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%2098%25%2C%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%20top%202%25%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20Rs%2064.3%20lakh%20crore%20or%20Rs%2023.8%20lakh%20per%20person.%20Their%20consumption%20was%2066.36%25%20of%20the%20total%20and%20they%20are%20the%20real%20polluters%20because%20they%20have%20the%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20luxury%20items%20and%20inessentials.%20The%20picture%20today%20will%20not%20be%20very%20different%20from%20that%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20in%20India%20are%20also%20recyclers%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20waste%20produced%20by%20the%20well-off.%20So%2C%20their%20net%20environmental%20impact%20is%20smaller%20than%20implied%20by%20their%20consumption.%20The%20poor%20do%20cut%20corners%20and%20pollute%20but%20that%20is%20done%20for%20survival%20and%20not%20for%20luxury.%20Finally%2C%20the%20poor%20are%20also%20forced%20to%20produce%20cheaply%20for%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consumption%20of%20the%20well-off%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20imports%20of%20automobiles%2C%20electronic%20items%2C%20specialty%20items%2C%20etc.%20Even%20when%20these%20are%20produced%20in%20the%20country%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20parts%20are%20imported.%20To%20balance%20trade%2C%20exports%20are%20required.%20India%20exports%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20low%20and%20intermediate%20technology%20products%20like%2C%20textiles%2C%20leather%20goods%20and%20toys%20where%20it%20faces%20competition%20from%20the%20other%20developing%20world%20nations.%20So%20prices%20have%20to%20be%20kept%20low%20(competitive).%20This%20is%20achieved%20by%20sacrificing%20environmental%20standards%20and%20paying%20workers%20low%20salaries.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20developing%20world%20accepts%20a%20polluted%20environment%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECOP%20not%20discussing%20the%20real%20issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028th%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20is%20taking%20place%20but%20the%20real%20step%20required%2C%20namely%2C%20cutting%20consumption%20globally%2C%20is%20not%20on%20the%20agenda.%20Use%20of%20cleaner%20energy%20sources%20will%20help%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20the%20free%20rider%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20each%20nation%20expects%20others%20to%20take%20the%20steps%20required.%20The%20rich%20nations%20are%20blaming%20India%20and%20China%20for%20being%20the%20big%20polluters%20now.%20The%20latter%20blame%20the%20rich%20nations%20for%20the%20historical%20accumulation%20of%20greenhouse%20gases%20and%20is%20asking%20them%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20and%20to%20make%20available%20new%20technologies%20to%20reduce%20production%20of%20greenhouse%20gases.%20The%20rich%20nations%20are%20not%20offering%20to%20lower%20their%20per%20capita%20consumption.%20They%20see%20this%20as%20a%20lowering%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20their%20people.%20The%20developing%20nations%20like%20India%20are%20not%20offering%20to%20pursue%20policies%20that%20would%20reduce%20the%20consumption%20of%20the%20well-off.%20They%20see%20this%20as%20a%20reduction%20of%20their%20growth%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20developing%20nations%20are%20protecting%20the%20interest%20of%20their%20corporations%20and%20their%20well-off%20whose%20growing%20consumption%20leads%20to%20higher%20profits.%20Both%20want%20to%20persist%20with%20growing%20consumption%20of%20their%20elite%2C%20corporate%20culture%20and%20wasteful%20governments.%20This%20shows%20where%20the%20real%20political%20power%20in%20the%20World%20lies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20slogan%201%25%20against%20the%2099%25%20is%20apt.%20The%20cost%20of%20deliberate%20obfuscation%20falls%20on%20the%20marginalised%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20the%20poorer%20nations%20or%20the%20poor%20in%20each%20of%20the%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20brief%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20growing%20pollution%20are%20upon%20us%20and%20imposing%20heavy%20costs%20on%20all.%20Yet%2C%20the%20political%20will%20to%20take%20the%20drastic%20steps%20required%20is%20missing.%20The%20time%20for%20taking%20incremental%20steps%20is%20over.%20The%20fear%20that%20cutting%20consumption%20and%20production%20will%20reduce%20welfare%20for%20the%20elite%20and%20reduce%20employment%20is%20unfounded%20because%20these%20can%20be%20achieved%20by%20cutting%20social%20waste%20and%20inessential%20consumption%20which%20will%20enhance%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20well-being%20by%20reducing%20pollution.%20A%20study%20from%20the%20SA%20showed%20that%20in%201980%2C%2050%25%20of%20the%20production%20was%20a%20waste.%20For%20India%2C%20in%202006%2C%2025%25%20was%20a%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20COP%20to%20make%20progress%2C%20the%20agenda%20of%20both%20the%20rich%20nations%20and%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20the%20developing%20countries%20has%20to%20be%20cutting%20wasteful%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EUnderstanding%20Black%20Economy%20and%20Black%20Money%20in%20India%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702380623000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12153224%2Fmike-marrah-x4QaRXytmow-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcop-protecting-the-lifestyle-of-the-well-off-for-the-28th-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20COP%20to%20make%20progress%2C%20the%20agenda%20of%20both%20the%20rich%20nations%20and%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20the%20developing%20countries%20has%20to%20be%20cutting%20wasteful%20consumption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22