hhar-in-fraud-case-123121200616_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chanda%20Kochhar%20and%20her%20husband%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20December%2023%2C%202022%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Videocon-ICICI%20Bank%20loan%20case%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-defers-hearing-on-cbi-plea-against-bail-to-chanda-kochhar-in-fraud-case-123121200616_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-defers-hearing-on-cbi-plea-against-bail-to-chanda-kochhar-in-fraud-case-123121200616_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-defers-hearing-on-cbi-plea-against-bail-to-chanda-kochhar-in-fraud-case-123121200616_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Was%20Removed%2C%20Kohli%20Was%20Made%20VC...%26quot%3B%3A%20Gambhir's%20Viral%20Video%20Resurfaces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20straight%20and%20honest%20talker.%20He%20has%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20making%20honest%20comments%2C%20even%20if%20that%20has%20led%20to%20controversies.%20The%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20opener%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%202007%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup-winning%20teams%2C%20was%20never%20a%20skipper%20for%20the%20national%20side.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20IPL%20he%20led%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20to%20the%20title.%20Recently%20an%20old%20video%20went%20viral%20on%20the%20social%20media%2C%20where%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20could%20be%20seen%20talking%20about%20his%20removed%20as%20vice-captain%20after%20India%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%20of%20the%20CB%20series.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20was%20done%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTNVkjEMFIeA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELallantop%3C%2Fa%3E%20YouTube%20channel%C2%A0%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20was%20re-shared%20by%20them%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CB%20series%20that%20was%20talking%20about%2C%20India%20did%20not%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%2C%20Australia%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20did.%20I%20was%20the%20vice-captain%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20the%20captain.%20After%20that%20series%20were%20supposed%20to%20travel%20for%20a%20tri-series%20involving%20India%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Bangladesh.%20We%20had%20not%20qualified%20for%20the%20final%2C%20before%20that%20%C2%A0we%20had%20lost%20the%20Test%20series%204-0.%20Dhoni%20was%20also%20under%20pressure%2C%20he%20was%20the%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20said%20in%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20something%20was%20changed%20after%20the%20CB%20series%20it%20was%20the%20vice-captain.%20I%20was%20removed%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20made%20the%20vice-captain.%20In%20the%20history%20of%20India%20or%20any%20sport%2C%20has%20it%20happened%20even%20once%20when%20the%20vice-captain%20was%20removed%20but%20the%20captain%20was%20intact.%20You%20can%20confront%20me%2C%20if%20I%20am%20wrong.%20Duncan%20Fletcher%20was%20the%20coach%20then.%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20was%20the%20reason%20behind%20that%20decision.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20the%20selectors'%20decision.%20I%20then%20asked%20him%20'For%20what%2C%20%C2%A0then%2C%20did%20you%20go%20to%20the%20meeting%3F%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20opined%20that%20Rohit%20should%20lead%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20if%20he%20is%20in%20good%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20in%20good%20form%2C%20he%20should%20be%20leading%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20or%20if%20he%20is%20not%20in%20good%20form%2C%20whoever%20is%20not%20in%20good%20form%20should%20not%20be%20picked%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Captaincy%20is%20a%20responsibility.%20First%2C%20you%20get%20yourself%20selected%20as%20a%20player%20and%20then%20you're%20made%20captain.%20A%20captain%20should%20have%20a%20permanent%20position%20in%20the%20playing%20eleven%2C%20and%20the%20permanent%20place%20depends%20on%20the%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20told%20ANI%20in%20a%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20winner%20said%20that%20age%20should%20not%20be%20a%20criterion%20when%20dropping%20a%20player%20from%20the%20squad%20and%20form%20should%20be%20the%20only%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAge%20should%20not%20be%20the%20criteria%20why%20a%20player%20should%20be%20dropped%20or%20picked%2C%20only%20form%20should%20be%20the%20criteria.%20Retirement%20is%20also%20an%20individual%20decision%2C%20no%20one%20can%20force%20him%20(a%20player)%20to%20retire%2C%20selectors%20have%20all%20the%20right%20not%20to%20pick%20them%20but%20ultimately%20one%20cannot%20take%20a%20bat%20or%20ball%20away%20from%20a%20player.%20Form%20is%20the%20topmost%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20had%20a%20stellar%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20for%20the%20'Men%20in%20Blue'%20as%20an%20opener.%20The%2036-year-old%20was%20the%20second-most%20run-getter%20in%20the%20tournament.%20He%20set%20the%20pace%20for%20India's%20innings%20in%20matches%20and%20scored%20597%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20125.94%20in%2011%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702379280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-09%2Fgautam-gambhir-virat-kohli_650x400_61475233163.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-was-removed-virat-kohli-was-made-vice-captain-gautam-gambhirs-video-with-ms-dhoni-resurfaces-goes-viral-4659867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20making%20honest%20comments%2C%20even%20if%20that%20has%20led%20to%20controversies%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-was-removed-virat-kohli-was-made-vice-captain-gautam-gambhirs-video-with-ms-dhoni-resurfaces-goes-viral-4659867%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-was-removed-virat-kohli-was-made-vice-captain-gautam-gambhirs-video-with-ms-dhoni-resurfaces-goes-viral-4659867%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-was-removed-virat-kohli-was-made-vice-captain-gautam-gambhirs-video-with-ms-dhoni-resurfaces-goes-viral-4659867%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%20updates%3A%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20is%20BJP's%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20choice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702379015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F06%2Ffull%2F1699293666-5979.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-dec-12-todays-breaking-news-updates-123121200111_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Catch%20the%20latest%20news%20updates%20from%20across%20the%20world%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flat