t%20delays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702378252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fhp%2Fhome-page%2F2022-01%2F30%2Ffull%2F1643566820-2477.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-ordered-to-pay-rs-2-lakh-to-passengers-for-multiple-flight-delays-123121200697_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NCDRC%20said%20in%20its%20order%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20flight%20cancellations%20or%20major%20delays%2C%20passengers%20are%20entitled%20to%20necessary%20services%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-ordered-to-pay-rs-2-lakh-to-passengers-for-multiple-flight-delays-123121200697_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBRS%20Left%20Telangana%20Bankrupt%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20Alleges%20Wasteful%20Spends%2C%20Corruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20took%20charge%20of%20India's%20youngest%20state%2C%20a%20senior%20minister%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20-%20which%20ruled%20for%2010%20years%20-%20has%20left%20Telangana%20bankrupt%20and%20indulged%20in%20wasteful%20expenditure%20as%20well%20as%20corruption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20and%20has%20been%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20Irrigation%2C%20Food%20and%20Civil%20Supplies%20portfolios%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20government%20has%20also%20left%20behind%20a%20heavy%20loan%20burden%2C%20which%20will%20lead%20to%20high%20interest%20payouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20review%20of%20the%20civil%20supplies%20department%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%20it%20has%20an%20outstanding%20loan%20of%20Rs%2056%2C000%20crore%2C%20partly%20because%20the%20BRS%20government%20did%20not%20give%20the%20department%20the%20ration%20subsidy%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20the%20interest%20on%20this%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20loan%20repayment%2C%20will%20be%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20annually.%20The%20BRS%20government%2C%20which%20ruled%20the%20state%20for%2010%20years%2C%20bankrupted%20the%20state%20financially.%20They%20indulged%20in%20very%20wasteful%20and%20non-productive%20expenditure%2C%20as%20well%20as%20corruption%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20said%20a%20review%20of%20the%20irrigation%20payment%20revealed%20an%20outstanding%20payment%20of%20bills%20worth%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20and%20that%20of%20the%20electricity%20department%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Anamula%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20revealed%20loans%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2081%2C000%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20wasteful%20expenditure%20in%20every%20sector%20and%20they%20(the%20BRS)%20have%20taken%20huge%20loans...%20They%20have%20left%20behind%20a%20financial%20mess%20and%20we%20will%20clean%20that%20up%20and%20take%20the%20state%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoney%20For%20Guarantees%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20planks%20behind%20the%20Congress'%20success%20in%20Telangana%20has%20been%20the%20six%20guarantees%20that%20the%20party%20had%20promised%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%20The%20guarantees%20include%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20for%20eligible%20women%2C%20free%20bus%20travel%20for%20women%2C%20200%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%2C%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500%2C%2024-hour%20power%20to%20farmers%20and%20Rs%204%2C000%20monthly%20pension%20for%20eligible%20senior%20citizens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20guarantees%20were%20approved%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20hours%20after%20being%20sworn%20in%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20question%20that%20everyone%20has%20asked%20is%20how%20the%20party%20intends%20to%20find%20the%20money%20to%20fund%20the%20schemes%20if%20the%20state's%20coffers%20are%20depleted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20question%20was%20posed%20to%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20Karnataka%20or%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20Congress%20means%20credibility...%20The%20guarantees%20were%20given%20by%20our%20supreme%20leaders%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarujun%20Kharge.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20implementing%20the%20guarantees%20within%20100%20days%20of%20the%20government's%20formation.%20We%20have%20implemented%20two%20guarantees%20in%20two%20days%20and%20I%20have%20reviewed%20two%20more%20today.%20We%20will%20definitely%20fulfil%20our%20promise%20despite%20financial%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20subsidised%20gas%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20will%20only%20be%20given%20to%20families%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%20and%20that%20the%20scheme%20will%20cost%20the%20government%20around%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIrrigation%20Project%20Probe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20sinking%20of%20the%20pillars%20of%20the%20Medigadda%20Barrage%2C%20part%20of%20the%20BRS'%20flagship%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20Kaleshwaram%20Multi-Lift%20Irrigation%20Project%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%20the%20government%20will%20order%20an%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20KCR%20government's%20way%20of%20working.%20They%20had%20claimed%20it%20is%20the%20world's%20best%20multi-purpose%20lift%20irrigation%20scheme.%20We%20have%20been%20saying%20there%20has%20been%20corruption%20in%20the%20project%20and%20that%20the%20construction%20was%20of%20poor%20quality%20and%20it%20had%20poor%20design.%20This%20was%20proved%20true%20when%2C%20a%20month%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20two%20pillars%20of%20the%20barrage%20sunk%20two%20metres%20into%20the%20ground%20and%20the%20water%20had%20to%20be%20drained%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20barrage%20project%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Kaleshwaram%20project.%20The%20faulty%20design%20was%20done%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20cabinet%20will%20have%20to%20hold%20the%20people%20responsible%20accountable%20for%20the%20loss%20to%20the%20state%20and%20its%20people.%20We%20will%20order%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20project%20and%20also%20review%20whether%20it%20is%20sustainable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702378140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F59glm1mg_uttam-kumar-reddy_625x300_12_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrs-left-telangana-bankrupt-congress-alleges-wasteful-spending-corruption-4659802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%20took%20charge%20of%20India's%20youngest%20state%2C%20a%20senior%20minister%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20which%20ruled%20for%2010%20years%2C%20has%20left%20Telangana%20bankrupt%20and%20indulged%20in%20wasteful%20expenditure%20as%20well%20as%20corruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrs-left-telangana-bankrupt-congress-alleges-wasteful-spending-corruption-4659802%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrs-left-telangana-bankrupt-congress-alleges-wasteful-spending-corruption-4659802%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrs-left-telangana-bankrupt-congress-alleges-wasteful-spending-corruption-4659802%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%2023%20soldiers%20killed%2