2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688837%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBenjamin%20Zephaniah.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BZephaniah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20radiant%20presence%20and%20a%20gentleman.%20Zephaniah%20was%20not%20in%20the%20least%20condescending%20to%20someone%20like%20me%20who%20was%20yet%20to%20publish%20anything%20besides%20occasional%20poetry%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20very%20refreshing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workshop%20Chatterji%20was%20conducting%2C%20along%20with%20bookmaker%20Priya%20Pereira%2C%20focussed%20on%20the%20joys%20of%20writing%20a%20nonsense%20rhyme%20and%20creating%20a%20book.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20adults%20were%20very%20cynical%20about%20nonsense%20poetry%2C%E2%80%9D%20remembers%20Chatterji%2C%20who%20would%20in%202004%20publish%20an%20English%20translation%20of%20Bengali%20poet%20Sukumar%20Ray%E2%80%99s%20legendary%20book%20of%20nonsense%20rhymes%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAbol%20Tabol%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20explain%20in%20great%20detail%20how%20nonsense%20poetry%20makes%20children%20use%20parts%20of%20their%20brain%20to%20understand%20language.%20Zephaniah%2C%20however%2C%20knew%20immediately%20what%20I%20was%20talking%20about.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20vitality%20is%20what%20I%20remember%20from%20so%20many%20years%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZephaniah%E2%80%99s%20vitality%20also%20made%20quite%20an%20impression%20on%20me%20when%20I%20heard%20him%20at%20my%20alma%20mater%2C%20Jadavpur%20University%20in%20Kolkata.%20This%20was%20during%20another%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20India.%20Trying%20to%20confirm%20my%20memories%2C%20I%20called%20my%20professor%20Abhijit%20Gupta%20who%20is%20a%20senior%20faculty%20member%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20English%20of%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20March%202007%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20told%20me.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20after%20the%20Nandigram%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2014%20that%20year%2C%20the%20police%20opened%20fire%20on%20farmers%20protesting%20against%20attempts%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20then%20under%20the%20Left%20Front%2C%20to%20acquire%20land%20and%20create%20a%20special%20economic%20zone%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Nandigram%2C%20about%20130%20km%20southwest%20of%20Kolkata.%20Fourteen%20farmers%20were%20killed%20and%20100%20were%20reported%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20and%20some%20faculty%20members%20at%20Jadavpur%20University%20were%20protesting%20against%20the%20violence.%20The%20state-wide%20protests%20around%20Nandigram%20and%20Singur%2C%20another%20village%20where%20the%20government%20was%20trying%20to%20acquire%20land%2C%20would%20snowball%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20would%2C%20in%202011%2C%20lead%20to%20the%20leftist%20state%20government%20being%20voted%20out%20after%2034%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20introducing%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gupta.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20told%20the%20audience%3A%20%E2%80%98Keep%20your%20questions%20short.%E2%80%99%20Zephaniah%2C%20who%20was%20more%20than%206%20feet%20tall%20and%20towered%20over%20me%2C%20replied%20without%20missing%20a%20beat%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20like%20my%20questions%20big%20and%20muscular.%E2%80%99%20The%20audience%20erupted%20into%20peals%20of%20laughter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20listening%20to%20him%20perform%20his%20poem%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da3HjMcY50Kc%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%253Da3HjMcY50Kc%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1702438151803000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1lYRIuEwd3DquR9pZK91sL%5C%22%3ERong%20Radio%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20visceral%20critique%20of%20state-sponsored%20propaganda.%20Now%2C%2015%20years%20later%2C%20as%20the%20media%20landscape%20around%20the%20world%20is%20roiled%20by%20viscous%20disinformation%20campaigns%2C%20Zephaniah%E2%80%99s%20words%20ring%20out%20with%20disquieting%20clarity%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20really%20did%20believe%20that%20terrorism%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20by%20governments%3Cbr%3E%5CnNot%20our%20government%2C%20not%20white%20government%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20just%20could%20not%20see%20what%20was%20wrong%20with%20me%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20gave%20hungry%20people%20hamburgers%20you%20see%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20was%20beginning%20to%20believe%20that%20our%20children%20were%20better%20than%20their%20children%3Cbr%3E%5CnTheir%20children%20would%20die%20from%20terrorism%20but%20i%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20their%20children%20call%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20a%20child%20from%20Palastine%20simply%20didn%E2%80%99t%20count%20at%20all%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhat%20despair%3Cbr%3E%5CnNo%20children%20i%20was%20not%20aware%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%E2%80%99d%20been%20listening%20to%20the%20wrong%20radio%20station%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUttaran%20Das%20Gupta%20is%20a%20New%20Delhi-based%20writer%20and%20journalist.%20He%20teaches%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University%2C%20Sonipat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702377051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F12145630%2FScreenshot-2023-12-12-at-2.56.03-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fremembering-benjamin-zephaniah-a-griot-in-the-world%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zephaniah%E2%80%99s%20radical%20rejection%20of%20mid-20th%20century%20abstract%20aestheticism%20in%20Western%20poetry%20has%20been%20much%20commented%20upon%20since%20his%20death%20recently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fremembering-benjamin-zephaniah-a-griot-in-the-world%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group's%20Ties%20with%20Controversial%20Contractor%20Howe%20Raise%20Governance%20Concerns%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17154946%2Fimage-1516.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Adani%20Group%20maintains%20ties%20with%20the%20controversial%20contracting%20firm%2C%20Howe%20Engineering%20Projects%20(India)%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20Taiwanese%20family%2C%20raising%20governance%20concerns%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-12-12%2Fadani-contractor-probed-by-india-resurfaces-under-a-new-name%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-contractor-probed-by-india-resurfaces-under-a-new-name-11702362098726.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20contracting%20firm%20contains%20the%20core%20operations%20of%20a%20business%20called%20PMC%20Projects%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPMC%20Projects%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20firms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsecond-inflated-imports-case-adani-struck%5C%22%3Ewas%20accused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20inflating%20the%20value%20of%20imported%20power%20and%20infrastructure%20goods%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20nearly%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20alleged%20that%20the%20firm%20was%20being%20used%20by%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20empire%20to%20siphon%20money%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20denied%20all%20wrongdoing%20and%20the%20probe%E2%80%99s%20findings%20were%20dismissed%20in%202017%20by%20the%20adjudicating%20authority%20of%20DRI%20(%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDirectorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E)%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-dismisses-plea-claiming-overvaluation-in-imported-goods-by-adani-123032800508_1.html%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20the%20imports%20were%20genuine.%20It%20concluded%20that%20the%20value%20declared%20was%20correct%20and%20was%20not%20required%20to%20be%20re-determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20filings%20indicate%20that%20in%20April%202016%2C%20PMC%E2%80%99s%20engineering%20business%20was%20integrated%20into%20Howe.%20Recent%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20analyses%20of%20filings%20reveal%20that%20Howe%20continues%20to%20serve%20as%20an%20Adani%20contractor%20for%20some%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20ports%20and%20railway%20lines%20currently%20under%20construction%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Deloitte%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20determine%20whether%20Howe%20should%20be%20labelled%20a%20related%20party%20was%20why%20the%20auditor%20raised%20red%20flags%20about%20payments%20by%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20ports%20company%20to%20the%20contracting%20firm%20in%20May%2C%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accounting%20giant%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fdeloitte-resigns-as-the-statutory-auditors-of-adani-ports-and-special-economic-zone%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20auditor%20for%20Adani%20Ports%20%26amp%3B%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd.%20in%20August%2C%20saying%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20sufficiently%20wide%20oversight%20over%20the%20broader%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Hindenburg%20Research%20directly%20called%20out%20PMC%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20alleging%20it%20was%20an%20Adani%20related%20party%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20suck%20money%20out%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20publicly%20listed%20entities.%E2%80%9D%20Its%20report%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20Howe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindenburg%20report%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CPMC%20Projects%20%E2%80%93%20a%20major%20contractor%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20%E2%80%93%20generated%20Rs%2063%20Billion%20(%24784%20Million)%20in%20revenue%20in%20the%20past%2012%20years.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20entity%20lacks%20a%20website.%20Records%20indicate%20its%20association%20with%20Adani%2C%20sharing%20the%20corporate%20address%20and%20phone%20number%20with%20the%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20short-seller%20had%20also%20sought%20clarification%20on%20whether%20PMC%20Projects%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdummy%20firm%E2%80%9D%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Adani%20conglomerate%20told%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Howe%20and%20PMC%20are%20independently%20operated%20and%20managed%20companies%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20Adani%20related%20parties%20and%20all%20transactions%20are%20compliant%20with%20the%20law.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20commercial%20and%20business%20transactions%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Adani%20entities%20for%20project%20management%20services%20were%20entered%20into%20in%20the%20ordinary%20course%20of%20business%20at%20arm%E2%80%99s%20length%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%E2%80%99s%20son%20owns%20PMC%20Projects%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US-based%20short%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20has%20been%20alleged%20to%20have%20made%20considerable%20profits%20by%20buying%20and%20selling%20Adani%20stock%20through%20offshore%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20companies%20designate%20contractors%20as%20related%20parties%20in%20their%20accounting%20procedures%2C%20payments%20go%20through%20scrutiny%20from%20auditors%20and%20the%20board.%20However%2C%20as%20Adani%20maintains%20that%20Howe%20and%20PMC%20are%20not%20related%20parties%2C%20the%20group%20is%20exempt%20from%20subjecting%20Howe%20payments%20to%20additional%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%20the%20office%20of%20Hi%20Lingos%20Co%20Ltd.%2C%20where%20Chung-ling%2C%20the%20father%2C%20is%20the%20registered%20owner%20in%20Taiwan.%20The%20office%20prominently%20displayed%20the%20Adani%20logo.%20An%20office%20secretary%20said%20that%20Chung-ling%20declined%20an%20interview.%20When%3Cem%3E%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20a%20provided%20number%20for%20the%20son%2C%20the%20person%20who%20answered%20initially%20questioned%20the%20source%20of%20the%20number%20but%20later%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20not%20Chang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20had%20never%20publicly%20disclosed%20the%20payments%20to%20Howe%20until%20Deloitte%20flagged%20them%20in%20May%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20%24245%20million%20of%20refundable%20deposits%20was%20returned%20by%20Howe%20to%20Adani%20since%20then.%20Contractors%20typically%20return%20these%20funds%20once%20a%20project%20is%20completed%20or%20terminated%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20is%20who%20is%20getting%20the%20money%2C%20what%20work%20are%20they%20doing%20for%20Howe%20and%20Adani%2C%20how%20is%20the%20money%20being%20spent%3F%E2%80%9D%20Sharmila%20Gopinath%2C%20a%20specialist%20advisor%20for%20India%20at%20the%20Hong%20Kong-based%20Asian%20Corporate%20Governance%20Association%2C%20asked%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20reason%20is%20there%20not%20to%20disclose%20these%20payments%20when%20there%20are%20obviously%20deep%20ties%20with%20these%20people%2C%20with%20the%20owner%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20says%20that%20Howe%20is%20not%20a%20connected%20entity%2C%20but%20governance%20expert%20Gopinath%20contends%20that%20the%20significant%20payments%20made%20by%20Adani%20to%20the%20contractor%2C%20whose%20ultimate%20owners%20are%20Taiwanese%20associates%2C%20should%20have%20been%20declared%20as%20related%20party%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20rules%20on%20the%20matter%20can%20be%20open%20to%20interpretation%3B%20disclosure%20is%20required%20for%20transactions%20where%20one%20party%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20control%20or%20significantly%20influence%20the%20other%E2%80%99s%20financial%20and%20operational%20decisions%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccounting%20experts%20suggest%20that%20shared%20resources%2C%20employees%2C%20or%20directors%20overseeing%20common%20projects%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20related%20parties%2C%20subjecting%20payments%20to%20additional%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20board%20and%20auditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20the%20filings%20to%20highlight%20a%20revolving%20door%20of%20employees%20between%20Adani%2C%20Howe%2C%20and%20PMC%2C%20with%20past%20directors%20from%20Howe%20and%20PMC%20also%20appointed%20to%20Adani%20group%20company%20boards%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopinath%20told%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20more%20scrutiny%20is%20needed%20across%20India%20to%20assess%20payments%20by%20listed%20companies%20because%20investor%20money%20is%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702377034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17154946%2Fimage-1516.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-groups-ties-with-controversial-contractor-howe-raise-governance-concerns-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bloomberg%20reported%20that%20the%20contracting%20firm%20contains%20the%20core%20operations%20of%20a%20business%20called%20PMC%20Projects%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20PMC%20Projects%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20firms%2C%20faced%20allegations%20of%20inflating%20the%20value%20of%20imported%20power%20and%20infrastructure%20goods%2C%20amounting%20to%20nearly%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-groups-ties-with-controversial-contractor-howe-raise-governance-concerns-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JNU%20Institutes%20New%20Rules%20to%20Punish%20Protests%20with%20Fines%2C%20Rustication%20from%20Campus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F06144304%2Fdu-protest.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20known%20for%20its%20robust%20student%20movements%2C%20will%20now%20penalise%20protests%20on%20campus%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20according%20to%20new%20rules%20released%20by%20the%20university%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rules%20of%20Discipline%20and%20Proper%20Conduct%20of%20Students%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20by%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%E2%80%99s%20Office%20were%20approved%20by%20the%20University%E2%80%99s%20Executive%20Council%20on%20November%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manual%20states%20that%20based%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20actions%20either%20one%20or%20two%20punishments%20will%20be%20handed%20out%2C%20which%20include%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%3B%20up%20to%20two%20semester%E2%80%99s%20eviction%20from%20the%20hostel%2C%20rustication%2C%20and%20declaring%20out%20of%20bounds%20from%20entire%20JNU%20campus%20for%20up%20to%20two%20semesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEither%20one%20or%20two%20of%20these%20punishments%20will%20be%20handed%20out%20for%20%E2%80%9Chunger%20strikes%2C%20dharnas%2C%20group%20bargaining%20and%20any%20other%20form%20of%20protest%20within%20a%20100-metre%20radius%20of%20any%20academic%20and%20administrative%20complexes%20and%2For%20by%20blocking%20entrance%20or%20exit%20of%20any%20academic%20and%20administrative%20complexes%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdisrupting%20the%20movement%20of%20any%20member%20of%20the%20University%20community%20in%20administration%2C%20academic%20complexes%2C%20etc%E2%80%9D%2C%20violation%20of%20rules%2Forders%2Fcirculars%20of%20competent%20authority%2C%20Obstruction%2Fdamage%20of%20electronic%20devices%20(i.e.%20camera%2C%20phone%2C%20etc.)%20at%20the%20time%20of%20evidence%20collection%20by%20security%20staff%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20manual%20also%20provides%20for%20stringent%20punishment%20for%20%E2%80%9Call%20acts%20of%20violence%20and%20all%20forms%20of%20coercion%20such%20as%20gheraos%2C%20sit-ins%20or%20any%20variation%20of%20the%20same%20which%20disrupt%20the%20normal%20academic%20and%20administrative%20functioning%20of%20the%20University%20and%2For%20any%20act%20which%20incites%20or%20leads%20to%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20gheraos%2C%20laying%20siege%20or%20staging%20demonstrations%20around%20the%20residence%20of%20any%20member%20of%20the%20University%20Community%20or%20any%20other%20form%20of%20coercion%2C%20intimidation%20or%20disturbance%20of%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20campus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20actions%20will%20attract%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20following%20punishments%20including%20a%20fine%20of%20upto%20Rs%2020%2C000%2C%20withdrawal%20of%20hostel%20facility%2C%20cancellation%20of%20admission%20or%20withdrawal%20of%20degree%20or%20denial%20of%20registration%20for%20a%20specified%20period%2C%20rustication%20and%20declaring%20out%20of%20bounds%20from%20entire%20JNU%20campus%20up%20to%20four%20semesters%2C%20expulsion%20from%20the%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEither%20one%20or%20two%20of%20these%20punishments%20will%20also%20be%20handed%20out%20for%20possession%20of%20illegal%20arms%2C%20any%20intimidation%20or%20insulting%20behaviour%20towards%20students%20or%20staff%2C%20wrongful%20confinement%20of%20staff%20or%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20states%20that%20the%20punishments%20may%20be%20applied%20for%20%E2%80%9Cany%20other%20act%20which%20may%20be%20considered%20by%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20or%20any%20other%20competent%20authority%20to%20be%20an%20act%20of%20violation%20of%20discipline%20and%20conduct.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20also%20state%20that%20students%20may%20face%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%206%2C000%20and%2For%20may%20have%20to%20carry%20out%20JNU%20community%20service%20for%20%E2%80%9Corganising%20events%20such%20as%20freshers%E2%80%99%20welcome%20parties%2C%20farewells%20or%20DJ%20events%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20campus%20without%20prior%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAimed%20at%20stifling%20vibrant%20campus%20culture%3A%20JNUSU%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNUSU%20(the%20students%E2%80%99%20body)%20of%20the%20campus%20has%20condemned%20the%20new%20rules%20and%20demanded%20that%20they%20be%20revoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNUSU%20said%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20brought%20in%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20any%20discussion%20or%20deliberation%20with%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20the%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20manual%20grants%20unprecedented%20powers%20to%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%2C%20compromising%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20student%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20stringent%20measures%20outlined%20in%20the%20manual%20are%20aimed%20at%20stifling%20the%20vibrant%20campus%20culture%20that%20has%20defined%20JNU%20for%20decades.%20Such%20excessive%20regulations%20are%20intended%20to%20discourage%20open%20discussions%2C%20dissent%2C%20and%20intellectual%20exploration%2C%20which%20are%20fundamental%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20our%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNUSU%20said%20that%20the%20manual%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20students%20are%20facing%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20academic%20and%20infrastructural%20issues%20in%20the%20campus%E2%80%9D%20including%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20journals%2C%20disrupted%20water%20supply%2C%20crumbling%20hostel%20buildings%2C%20delayed%20hostel%20admissions%2C%20and%20shortened%20semesters%2C%20among%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20repeated%20demands%20from%20the%20student%20community%2C%20the%20university%20administration%20has%20been%20unjustly%20delaying%20the%20conduct%20of%20student%20union%20elections%2C%20which%20has%20been%20stalled%20for%20four%20years%20now.%20The%20attack%20on%20the%20Student%20Union%20and%20student%20activism%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20very%20democratic%20ethos%20that%20has%20built%20the%20university%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20note%20in%20the%20foreword%20to%20the%20manual%20Chief%20Proctor%20Prof.%20N.%20Janardhana%20Raju%20said%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20brought%20in%20because%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cstrongly%20felt%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20existing%20disciplinary%20rules%20be%20reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20strongly%20felt%20to%20review%20the%20existing%20disciplinary%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20Office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Proctor%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20foreward%20note%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20no%20substantially%20approved%20rules%20and%20regulations%20on%20proper%20conduct%20and%20discipline%20of%20students%20by%20the%20Statutory%20Body%20(i.e.%20Executive%20Council)%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20in%20vogue.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20undertake%20a%20careful%20preparation%20of%20Chief%20Proctor%20Office%20(CPO)%20manual%20encompassing%20rules%20and%20regulations%20to%20be%20followed%20during%20the%20proctorial%20enquiry%20based%20on%20the%20experiences%20accumulated%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20reached%20out%20to%20JNU%20vice%20chancellor%20Santishree%20Dhulipudi%20Pandit%20for%20a%20comment.%20This%20re