coaching%20institute%20where%20they%20had%20very%20less%20aspirants%2C%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20a%20class%20of%20400%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saloni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20only%20had%20five%20months%20to%20appear%20for%20prelims.%20I%20would%20seclude%20myself%20in%20a%20library%2C%20away%20from%20the%20chaos%20of%20aspirants%20who%20keep%20advising%20others%20to%20follow%20this%20or%20that%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-3-1700746961-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334807%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20advises%20UPSC%20aspirants%20to%20not%20follow%20a%20blanket%20approach.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELive%20in%20your%20comfort%20zone%20a%20month%20before%20the%20exam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%20says%20that%20she%20moved%20to%20her%20comfort%20zone%20%E2%80%94%20her%20home%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20last%20month%20before%20appearing%20fo